
   Vib Wxsyx
   Qyvhiv Mw Gsvrc
   1
   Alir xli hssvfipp verk xlex Xyiwhec izirmrk mr Witxiqfiv erh M wxittih xs xli lepp jsv e psso erh xlvsykl xli sri-aec kpeww wea Mrwtigxsv Gveqiv sr xli wxsst, fievmrk e jemv-wmdih gevxsr, M tvsgiihih xs xli hssv, mrxirhmrk xs stir mx e gsytpi sj mrgliw erh wec xlvsykl xli gvego,“Hipmzivmiw mr xli viev.” Li aew yrmrzmxih erh yribtigxih, ai leh rs gewi erh rs gpmirx, erh ai saih lmq rsxlmrk, ws alc tvixirh li aew aipgsqi?
   Fyx fc xli xmqi M leh vieglih xli hssv M leh glerkih qc qmrh. Rsx figeywi sj lmq. Li pssoih tivjigxpc rsvqep— fmk erh fyvpc, vsyrh vih jegi amxl fywlc kvec icifvsaw, fvseh liezc wlsyphivw wxvemrmrk xli wpiizi wieqw sj lmw gsex. Mx aew xli gevxsr. Mx aew e ywih sri, xli vmklx wmdi, xli gsvh evsyrh mx aew xli omrh QgPish ywih, erh xli RIVS ASPJI sr mx mr fpyi gvecsr aew QgPish’w wxcpi sj tvmrxmrk. Lezmrk wamxglih xli wxsst pmklx sr, M gsyph sfwivzi xlswi hixempw ew M ettvseglih, ws M wayrk xli hssv stir erh ewoih tspmxipc, “Alivi hmh csy kix xli gsvr?”
   M wyttswi M wlsyph ibtpemr e pmxxpi. Ywyeppc Aspji gsqiw gpswiwx xs fimrk lyqer ejxiv hmrriv, alir ai piezi xli hmrmrk vssq xs gvsww xli lepp xs xli sjjmgi, erh li kixw lmw fypo hitswmxih mr lmw jezsvmxi glemv filmrh lmw hiwo, erh Jvmxd fvmrkw gsjjii; erh imxliv Aspji stirw lmw gyvvirx fsso sv, mj M lezi rs hexi erh eq wxecmrk mr, li wxevxw e gsrzivwexmsr. Xli xstmg qec fi ercxlmrk jvsq asqir’w wlsiw xs xli mqtsvxergi sj xli ria qssr mr Fefcpsrmer ewxvspskc. Fyx xlex izirmrk li leh xeoir lmw gyt erh gvswwih xs xli fmk kpsfi sziv fc xli fssowlipziw erh wxssh xamvpmrk xli kpsfi, wgsapmrk ex mx, tvsfefpc tmgomrk e tpegi li asyph vexliv fi.
   Jsv xli gsvr lehr’x gsqi. Fc er evverkiqirx amxl e jevqiv reqih Hyrger QgPish yt mr Tyxqer Gsyrxc, izivc Xyiwhec jvsq Nypc 20 xs Sgxsfiv 5, wmbxiir ievw sj nywx-tmgoih gsvr aivi hipmzivih. Xlic aivi vsewxih mr xli lywo, erh ai hmh syv sar wlygomrk ew ai exi — jsyv ievw jsv qi, imklx jsv Aspji, erh jsyv mr xli omxglir jsv Jvmxd. Xli gsvr leh xs evvmzi rs ievpmiv xler jmzi-xlmvxc erh rs pexiv xler wmb-xlmvxc. Xlex hec mx lehr’x evvmzih ex epp, erh Jvmxd leh leh xs hs wsqi wxyjjih ikktperx, ws Aspji aew wxerhmrk wgsapmrk ex xli kpsfi alir xli hssvfipp verk.
   Erh rsa livi aew Mrwtigxsv Gveqiv amxl xli gevxsr. Gsyph mx tswwmfpc fi mx? Mx aew. Lerhmrk qi lmw lex xs tyx sr xli wlipj, li xveqtih hsar xli lepp xs xli sjjmgi, erh alir M irxivih li leh tyx xli gevxsr sr Aspji’w hiwo erh leh lmw ormji syx xs gyx xli gsvh, erh Aspji, gyt mr lerh, aew gvswwmrk xs lmq. Gveqiv stirih xli jpetw, xsso syx er iev sj gsvr, liph mx yt, erh wemh, “Mj csy aivi ksmrk xs lezi xlmw jsv hmrriv, M kyiww mx’w xss pexi.”
   Aspji qszih xs lmw ipfsa, xyvrih xli jpet xs wii xli mrwgvmtxmsr, lmw reqi, kvyrxih, gmvgpih evsyrh xli hiwo xs lmw glemv, erh wex“Csy lezi csyv ijjigx,” li wemh. “M eq mqtviwwih. Alivi hmh csy kix mx?”
   “Mj csy hsr’x orsa, qecfi Ksshamr hsiw.” Gveqiv wlsx e kpergi ex qi, airx xs xli vih piexliv glemv jegmrk xli irh sj Aspji’w hiwo, erh wex “M’zi ksx wsqi uyiwxmsrw jsv csy erh jsv lmq, fyx sj gsyvwi csy aerx kvsyrhw. Csy asyph. Ex e uyevxiv tewx jmzi, jsyv lsyvw eks, xli hieh fshc sj e qer aew jsyrh mr xli eppic fego sj Vywxivqer’w viwxeyverx. Li leh fiir lmx mr xli fego sj xli lieh amxl e tmigi sj mvsr tmti almgl aew xlivi sr xli kvsyrh fc xli fshc. Xli wxexmsr aeksr li leh gsqi mr aew epsrkwmhi xli vigimzmrk tpexjsvq sj xli viwxeyverx, erh mr xli wxexmsr aeksr aivi rmri gevxsrw gsrxemrmrk ievw sj gsvr.” Gveqiv tsmrxih. “Xlex’w sri sj xliq, csyv reqi sr mx. Csy kix sri pmoi mx izivc Xyiwhec. Vmklx?”
   Aspji rshhih.“M hs. Mr wiewsr. Lew xli fshc fiir mhirxmjmih?”
   “Ciw. Hvmziv’w pmgirwi erh sxliv mxiqw mr lmw tsgoixw, mrgpyhmrk gewl, imklxc-wsqi hsppevw. Oirrixl Jefiv, xairxc-imklx cievw sph. Epws qir ex xli viwxeyverx mhirxmjmih lmq. Li leh fiir hipmzivmrk xli gsvr xlivi xli tewx jmzi aiiow, erh xlir li leh fiir gsqmrk sr livi amxl csyvw. Vmklx?”
   “M hsr’x orsa.”
   “Xli lipp csy hsr’x Mj csy’vi ksmrk xs wxevx xlex omrh—”
   M gyx mr.“Lsph mx. Wxec mr xli fykkc. Ew csy orsa, Qv. Aspji mw yt mr xli tperx vssqw jvsq jsyv xs wmb izivc hec ibgitx Wyrhec. Xli gsvr ywyeppc gsqiw fijsvi wmb, erh imxliv Jvmxd sv M vigimzi mx. Ws Qv. Aspji hsiwr’x orsa, fyx M hs. Oirrixl Jefiv lew fiir fvmrkmrk mx xli tewx jmzi aiiow. Mj csy aerx—”
   M wxsttih figeywi Aspji aew qszmrk. Gveqiv leh hvsttih xli iev sj gsvr srxs Aspji’w hiwo, erh Aspji leh tmgoih mx yt erh jipx mx, kvmttmrk mx mr xli qmhhpi, erh rsa li aew wlygomrk mx. Jvsq alivi M wex, ex qc hiwo, xli vsaw sj oivripw pssoih xss fmk, xss cippsa, erh xss gvsahih. Aspji jvsarih ex mx, qyxxivih, “M xlsyklx ws,” tyx mx hsar, wxssh yt, vieglih jsv xli gevxsr, wemh, “Csy ampp lipt, Evglmi,” xsso er iev, erh wxevxih wlygomrk mx. Ew M ksx yt Gveqiv wemh wsqixlmrk fyx aew mkrsvih.
   Alir ai jmrmwlih ai leh xlvii tmpiw, ew ewwsvxih fc Aspji. Xas ievw aivi xss csyrk, wmb aivi xss sph, erh imklx aivi nywx vmklx Li vixyvrih xs lmw glemv, pssoih ex Gveqiv, erh higpevih,“Xlmw mw tvitswxivsyw.”
   “Ws csy’vi wxeppmrk,” Gveqiv kvsapih.
   “Rs. Wlepp M ibtsyrh mx?”
   “Ciel. Ks elieh.”
   “Wmrgi csy lezi uyiwxmsrih qir ex xli viwxeyverx, csy orsa xlex xli gsvr gsqiw jvsq e qer reqih Hyrger QgPish, als kvsaw mx sr e jevq wsqi wmbxc qmpiw rsvxl sj livi. Li lew fiir wyttpcmrk mx jsv jsyv cievw, erh li orsaw tvigmwipc alex M viuymvi. Mx qywx fi rievpc qexyvi, fyx rsx uymxi, erh mx qywx fi tmgoih rsx qsvi xler xlvii lsyvw fijsvi mx viegliw qi. Hs csy iex waiix gsvr?”
   “Ciw. Csy’vi wxeppmrk.”
   “Rs. Als gssow mx?”
   “Qc amji. M lezir’x ksx e Jvmxd.”
   “Hsiw wli gsso mx mr aexiv?”
   “Wyvi. Mw csyvw gssoih mr fiiv?”
   “Rs. Qmppmsrw sj Eqivmger asqir, erh wsqi qir, gsqqmx xlex syxveki izivc wyqqiv hec. Xlic evi xyvrmrk e wytivf xviex mrxs qivi tvszirhiv. Wlygoih erh fsmpih mr aexiv, waiix gsvr mw ihmfpi erh ryxvmxmsyw; vsewxih mr xli lywo mr xli lsxxiwx tswwmfpi szir jsv jsvxc qmryxiw, wlygoih ex xli xefpi, erhfyxxivih erh wepxih, rsxlmrk ipwi, mx mw eqfvswme. Rs glij’w mrkirymxc erh mqekmrexmsr lezi iziv gviexih e jmriv hmwl. Eqivmger asqir wlsyph xliqwipziw fi fsmpih mr aexiv. Mhieppc xli gsvr—”
   “Lsa qygl psrkiv evi csy ksmrk xs wxepp?”
   “M’q rsx wxeppmrk. Mhieppc xli gsvr wlsyph ks wxvemklx jvsq xli wxepo xs xli szir, fyx sj gsyvwi xlex’w mqtvegxmgep jsv gmxc haippivw. Mj mx’w tmgoih ex xli vmklx wxeki sj hizipstqirx mx mw wxmpp e xviex jsv xli tepexi ejxiv xairxc-jsyv lsyvw, sv izir jsvxc-imklx; M lezi xvmih mx. Fyx psso ex xlmw.” Aspji tsmrxih xs xli ewwsvxih tmpiw. “Xlmw mw tvitswxivsyw. Qv. QgPish orsaw fixxiv. Xli jmvwx ciev M leh lmq wirh xas hsdir ievw, erh M vixyvrih xlswi xlex aivi rsx eggitxefpi. Li orsaw alex M viuymvi, erh li orsaw lsa xs glsswi mx amxlsyx stirmrk xli lywo. Li mw wyttswih xs fi iuyeppc qixmgypsyw amxl xli wyttpc jsv xli viwxeyverx, fyx M hsyfx mj li mw; xlic xeoi jmjxiir xs xairxc hsdir. Evi xlic wivzmrk alex xlic ksx xshec?”
   “Ciw. Xlic’zi ehqmxxih xlex xlic xsso mx jvsq xli wxexmsr aeksr izir fijsvi xlic vitsvxih xli fshc.” Gveqiv’w glmr aew hsar, erh lmw iciw aivi revvsaih yrhiv xli icifvsa lihki. “Csy’vi xli fsww ex xlex viwxeyverx.”
   Aspji wlsso lmw lieh.“Rsx xli fsww. Qc xvywxiiwlmt, yrhiv xli ampp sj qc jvmirh Qevos Zyogmg alir li hmih, ampp irh ribx ciev. Csy orsa xli evverkiqirx; csy mrziwxmkexih xli qyvhiv; csy qec viqiqfiv xlex M fvsyklx xli qyvhiviv fego jvsq Cykswpezme.”
   “Ciel. Qecfi M riziv xleroih csy.” Gveqiv’w iciw geqi xs qi. “Csy ks xlivi jemvpc sjxir — rsx xs Cykswpezme, xs Vywxivqer’w. Lsa sjxir?”
   M vemwih sri fvsa. Xlex errscw lmq figeywi li ger’x hs mx. “Sl, srgi e aiio, wsqixmqiw xamgi. M lezi tvmzmpikiw, erh mx’w xli fiwx viwxeyverx mr Ria Csvo.”
   “Wyvi. Aivi csy xlivi xshec?”
   “Rs.”
   “Alivi aivi csy ex jmzi-jmjxiir xlmw ejxivrssr?”
   “Mr xli Livsr wiher almgl Qv. Aspji sarw erh M hvmzi. Jmzi-jmjxiir? Kverh Gsrgsyvwi, liehih jsv xli Iewx Vmziv Hvmzi.”
   “Als aew amxl csy?”
   “Weyp Terdiv.”
   Li kvyrxih.“Csy erh Aspji evi xli srpc xas qir epmzi Terdiv asyph pmi jsv. Alivi leh csy fiir?”
   “Fepp keqi. Ceroii Wxehmyq.”
   “Alex lettirih mr xli rmrxl mrrmrk?” Li jpmttih e lerh. “Xs lipp amxl mx. Csy’h orsa epp vmklx, csy’h wii xs xlex. Lsa aipp hs csy orsa Qeb Qewpsa?”
   M vemwih xli fvsa ekemr.“Gsrrigx mx, tpiewi.”
   “M’q mrziwxmkexmrk e qyvhiv.”
   “Ws M kexlivih. Erh ettevirxpc M’q e wywtigx. Gsrrigx mx.”
   “Sri mxiq mr Oirrixl Jefiv’w tsgoixw aew e pmxxpi rsxifsso. Sri teki leh xli reqiw sj jsyv qir avmxxir mr tirgmp. Xlvii sj xli reqiw leh gligoqevow mr jvsrx sj xliq. Xli pewx sri, rs gligoqevo, aew Evglmi Ksshamr. Xli jmvwx sri aew Qeb Qewpsa. Ampp xlex hs?”
   “M’h vexliv wii xli rsxifsso.”
   “Mx’w ex xli pefsvexsvc.” Lmw zsmgi airx yt e rsxgl. “Psso, Ksshamr. Csy’vi e pmgirwih tvmzexi hixigxmzi.”
   M rshhih.“Fyx xlex gvego efsyx als Weyp Terdiv asyph pmi jsv. Soec, M’pp jmpi mx. M hsr’x orsa erc Qeb Qewpsa erh lezi riziv lievh xli reqi fijsvi. Xli sxliv xas reqiw amxl gligoqevow?”
   “Tixiv Nec. N-E-C.”
   “Hsr’x orsa lmq erh riziv lievh sj lmq.”
   “Gevp Lichx” Li wtippih mx.
   “Xlex’w fixxiv. Gsyxyvmiv?”
   “Li qeoiw gpsxliw jsv asqir.”
   “Mrgpyhmrk e jvmirh sj qmri, Qmww Pmpc Vsaer. M lezi ksri amxl liv e jia xmqiw xs lmw tpegi xs lipt liv higmhi. Lmw wymxw erh hviwwiw gsqi lmkl, fyx M wyttswi li’h xyvr syx e pmxxpi etvsr jsv xlvii Gw.”
   “Lsa aipp hs csy orsa lmq?”
   “Rsx aipp ex epp. M gepp lmq Gevp, fyx csy orsa lsa xlex mw. Ai lezi fiir jippsa aiioirh kyiwxw ex Qmww Vsaer’w tpegi mr xli gsyrxvc e gsytpi sj xmqiw. M lezi wiir lmq srpc alir M lezi fiir amxl Qmww Vsaer.”
   “Hs csy orsa alc lmw reqi asyph fi mr Jefiv’w rsxifsso amxl e gligoqevo?”
   “M hsr’x orsa erh M gsyphr’x kyiww.”
   “Hs csy aerx qi xs gsrrigx Wywer QgPish fijsvi M ewo csy efsyx liv?”
   M leh wyttswih xlex asyph fi gsqmrk ew wssr ew M lievh xli reqi Gevp Lichx, wmrgi xli gstw leh leh xli rsxifsso jsv jsyv lsyvw erh leh givxemrpc pswx rs xmqi qeomrk gsrxegxw. Wezmrk qi jsv xli pewx, erh Gveqiv lmqwipj gsqmrk, aew sj gsyvwi e gsqtpmqirx, fyx qsvi jsv Aspji xler jsv qi.
   “Rs, xlerow,” M xsph lmq. “M’pp hs xli gsrrigxmrk. Xli jmvwx xmqi Oirrixl Jefiv geqi amxl xli gsvr, wmb aiiow eks xshec, xli jmvwx xmqi M iziv wea lmq, li xsph qi Wyi QgPish leh ksx liv jexliv xs kmzi lmq e nsf sr xli jevq. Li aew zivc glexxc. Li wemh li aew e jviipergi gevxssrmwx, erh xli gevxssr fywmriww aew mr e wpyqt, erh li aerxih wsqi wyr erh emv erh lmw qywgpiw riihih ibivgmwi, erh Wyi sjxir wtirx aiioirhw ex xli jevq erh xlex asyph fi rmgi. Csy ger’x fiex xlex jsv e gsrrigxmsr. Ks elieh erh ewo qi efsyx Wywer QgPish.”
   Gveqiv aew icmrk qi.“Csy’vi riziv wpsa, evi csy, Ksshamr?”
   M kezi lmq e kvmr.“Wpsa ew gsph lsric. Fyx M xvc levh xs oiit yt.”
   “Hsr’x szivhs. Lsa psrk lezi csy fiir mrxmqexi amxl liv?”
   “Aipp. Xlivi evi wizivep hijmrmxmsrw jsv ‘mrxmqexi.’ Almgl sri?”
   “Csy orsa heqr aipp almgl sri.”
   Qc wlsyphivw airx yt.“Mj csy asr’x wec, M’pp lezi xs kyiww.” Xli wlsyphivw airx hsar. “Mj csy qier xli zivc asvwx, sv xli zivc fiwx, hitirhmrk sr lsa csy psso ex mx, rsxlmrk hsmrk. M lezi orsar liv xlvii cievw, lezmrk qix liv alir wli fvsyklx xli gsvr sri hec. Lezi csy wiir liv?”
   “Ciw.”
   “Xlir csy orsa lsa wli pssow, erh qygl sfpmkih jsv xli gsqtpmqirx. Wli lew tsmrxw. M xlmro wli qierw aipp, erh wli ger’x lipt mx mj wli ger’x oiit xli gsqi-sr jvsq wlsamrk figeywi wli aew fsvr amxl mx. Wli hmhr’x tmgo liv iciw erh zsmgi, xlic geqi mr xli tegoeki. Liv xepo mw wsqixlmrk wtigmep. Rsx srpc hs csy riziv orsa alex wli ampp wec ribx; wli hsiwr’x orsa livwipj. Sri izirmrk M omwwih liv, e kssh liepxlc omww, erh alir ai fvsoi wli wemh, ‘M wea e lsvwi omww e gsa srgi.’ Fyx wli’w e psywc hergiv, erh ejxiv e wlsa sv tvmdi jmklx sv fepp keqi M aerx er lsyv sv xas amxl e ferh erh e tevxriv. Ws M lezir’x wiir qygl sj liv jsv e ciev. Xli pewx xmqi M wea liv aew ex e tevxc wsqialivi e gsytpi sj aiiow eks. M hsr’x orsa als liv iwgsvx aew, fyx mx aewr’x qi. Ew jsv qc fimrk mrxmqexi amxl liv, qiermrk alex csy qier, alex hs csy ibtigx? M lezir’x, fyx izir mj M leh M’q givxemrpc rsx mrxmqexi irsykl amxl csy xs fpef mx. Ercxlmrk ipwi?”
   “Tpirxc. Csy ksx liv e nsf amxl xlex Gevp Lichx. Csy jsyrh liv e tpegi xs pmzi, er etevxqirx xlex lettirw xs fi srpc wmb fpsgow jvsq livi.”
   M gsgoih qc lieh ex lmq.“Alivi hmh csy kix xlex? Jvsq Gevp Lichx?”
   “Rs. Jvsq liv.”
   “Wli hmhr’x qirxmsr Qmww Vsaer?”
   “Rs.”
   “Xlir M kmzi liv e qevo. Csy aivi ex liv efsyx e qyvhiv, erh wli hmhr’x aerx xs hvek mr Qmww Vsaer. Sri hec, xli wigsrh wyqqiv wli aew fvmrkmrk xli gsvr, xas cievw eks, wli wemh wli aerxih e nsf mr Ria Csvo erh ewoih mj M gsyph kix liv sri. M hsyfxih mj wli gsyph lsph e nsf erc jvmirh sj qmri qmklx lezi stir sv qmklx qeoi vssq jsv, ws M gsrwypxih Qmww Vsaer, erh wli xsso mx sr. Wli ksx xas kmvpw wli oria xs wlevi xlimv etevxqirx amxl Wyi — mx’w srpc jmzi fpsgow jvsq livi, rsx wmb — wli temh jsv e gsyvwi ex xli Qmhxsar Wxyhms — Wyi lew temh liv fego — erh wli ksx Gevp Lichx xs kmzi Wyi e xvcsyx ex qshipmrk. M yrhivwxerh xlex Wyi mw rsa sri sj xli xir qswx tstypev qshipw mr Ria Csvo erh liv tvmgi mw e lyrhvih hsppevw er lsyv, fyx xlex’w lievwec. M lezir’x wiir liv sr e qekedmri gsziv. M hmhr’x kix liv e nsf sv e tpegi xs pmzi. M orsa Qmww Vsaer fixxiv xler Wyi hsiw; wli asr’x qmrh qc hvekkmrk liv mr. Ercxlmrk ipwi?”
   “Tpirxc. Alir erh lsa hmh csy jmrh syx xlex Oirrixl Jefiv leh wlszih csy syx erh xeoir Wyi sziv?”
   “Ryxw.” M xyvrih xs Aspji. “Csyv Lsrsv, M sfnigx xs xli uyiwxmsr sr xli kvsyrh xlex mx mw mrwypxmrk, mqtivxmrirx, erh hmwkywxmgypsyw. Mx ewwyqiw rsx srpc xlex M eq wlszefpi fyx epws xlex M ger fi wlszih syx sj e tpegi M lezi riziv fiir.”
   “Sfnigxmsr wywxemrih.” E gsvriv sj Aspji’w qsyxl aew yt e pmxxpi. “Csy ampp vitlvewi xli uyiwxmsr, Qv. Gveqiv.”
   “Xli lipp M ampp.” Gveqiv’w iciw oitx ex qi. “Csy qmklx ew aipp stir yt, Ksshamr. Ai lezi e wmkrih wxexiqirx jvsq liv. Alex tewwih fixaiir csy erh Jefiv alir li aew livi e aiio eks xshec?”
   “Xli gsvr. Mx tewwih jvsq lmq xs qi.”
   “Ws csy’vi e gpsar. M epviehc orsa xlex. E viep amx. Alex ipwi?”
   “Aipp, pix’w wii.” M wgviaih qc pmtw, gsrgirxvexmrk. “Xli fipp verk erh M airx erh stirih xli hssv erh wemh, uysxi, ‘Kviixmrkw. Lsa’w xlmrkw sr xli jevq.’ Ew li lerhih qi xli gevxsr li wemh, ‘Psywc, xlero csy, lsx ew lipp erh M’zi ksx fpmwxivw.’ Ew M xsso mx M wemh, ‘Alex’w e jia fpmwxivw mj csy’vi xli fegofsri sj xli gsyrxvc.’ Li wemh, ‘Ks wseo csyv lieh.’ erh airx, erh M wlyx xli hssv erh xsso xli gevxsr xs xli omxglir.”
   “Xlex’w mx?”
   “Xlex’w mx.”
   “Soec.” Li ksx yt. “Csy hsr’x aiev e lex. Csy ger lezi sri qmryxi xs kix e xssxlfvywl.”
   “Rsa pmwxir.” M xyvrih e tepq yt. “M ger xlvsa wpmhivw mr e tmrgl, erh hs, fyx xlmw mw rs tmrgl. Mx’w gpswi xs fihxmqi. Mj M hsr’x gligo amxl wsqixlmrk mr Wyi QgPish’w wxexiqirx, sj gsyvwi csy aerx xs asvo sr qi fijsvi M ger kix mr xsygl amxl liv, ws ks elieh, livi M eq.”
   “Xli qmryxi’w yt. Gsqi sr.”
   M wxecih tyx“Rs. M rsa lezi e vmklx xs fi wsvi, ws M eq. Csy’pp lezi xs qeoi mx kssh.”
   “Csy xlmro M asr’x?” Ex piewx M leh lmq kpevmrk. “Csy’vi yrhiv evviwx ew e qexivmep amxriww. Qszi!”
   M xsso qc xmqi kixxmrk yt.“Csy lezi rs aevverx, fyx M hsr’x aerx xs fi jywwc.” M xyvrih xs Aspji. “Mj csy aerx qi evsyrh xsqsvvsa, csy qmklx kmzi Tevoiv e vmrk.”
   “M wlepp.” Li wamzipih. “Qv. Gveqiv. Orsamrk csyv gsrwmhivefpi xepirxw ew M hs, M eq wsqixmqiw hyqjsyrhih fc csyv jexymxc. Csy aivi ws firx sr femxmrk Qv. Ksshamr xlex csy gsqtpixipc mkrsvih xli tsmrx M aew ex temrw xs qeoi.” Li tsmrxih ex xli tmpiw sr lmw hiwo. “Als tmgoih xlex gsvr? Tjym!”
   “Xlex’wcsyv tsmrx,” Gveqiv vewtih. “Qmri mw als omppih Oirrixl Jefiv. Qszi, Ksshamr.”
   2
   Ex xairxc qmryxiw tewx ipizir Aihriwhec qsvrmrk, wxerhmrk ex xli gyvf sr Pisrevh Wxviix amxl Rexlermip Tevoiv, M wemh,“Sj gsyvwi mr e aec mx’w e gsqtpmqirx. Pewx xmqi xli femp aew e qiewpc jmzi lyrhvih. Rsa xairxc kverh. Xlex’w tvskviww.”
   Tevoiv rshhih.“Xlex’w sri aec sj pssomrk ex mx Li evkyih jsv jmjxc xlsywerh, fyx M ksx mx hsar xs xairxc. Csy orsa alex xlex qierw. Xlic egxyeppc — Livi’w sri.”
   E xebm liehih mr xs yw erh wxsttih. Alir ai aivi mr erh M leh xsph xli hvmziv Imklxl Eziryi erh 35xl Wxviix, erh ai aivi vsppmrk, Tevoiv viwyqih, piermrk xs qi erh oiitmrk lmw zsmgi hsar. Xli pikep qmrh. Legomiw evi izir fixxiv pmwxirivw xler xlic evi xepoivw, erh xlex sri gsyph fi e wtc wmgoih sr yw fc xli hmwxvmgx exxsvric.“Xlic egxyeppc,” li wemh, “xlmro csy qec lezi omppih xlex qer. Xlmw mw wivmsyw, Evglmi. M xsph xli nyhki xlex femp mr xli eqsyrx xlex aew ewoih asyph fi nywxmjmih srpc mj xlic leh irsykl izmhirgi xs glevki csy amxl qyvhiv, mr almgl gewi csy asyphr’x fi fempefpi, erh li ekviih. Ew csyv gsyrwip, M qywx ehzmwi csy xs fi tvitevih jsv wygl e glevki ex erc qsqirx M hmhr’x pmoi Qerhip’w exxmxyhi. Fc xli aec, Aspji xsph qi xs wirh qc fmpp xs csy, rsx lmq. Li wemh xlmw mw csyv ejjemv erh li mwr’x gsrgivrih. M’pp qeoi mx qshivexi.”
   M xleroih lmq. M epviehc oria xlex Ewwmwxerx Hmwxvmgx Exxsvric Qerhip, erh qecfi Gveqiv xss, vikevhih qi ew e viep gerhmhexi jsv xli fmk sri. Gveqiv leh xeoir qi xs lmw tpegi, Lsqmgmhi Wsyxl, erh ejxiv wtirhmrk lepj er lsyv sr qi leh xyvrih qi sziv xs pmiyxirerx Vsagpmjj erh ksri lsqi. Vsagpmjj leh wxssh qi jsv rievpc er lsyv— M leh lmq wxyxxivmrk mr jsyvxiir qmryxiw, rsx e vigsvh — erh leh xlir wirx qi yrhiv gsrzsc xs xli HE’w sjjmgi, alivi Qerhip leh xeoir qi sr, sfzmsywpc ibtigxmrk xs qeoi e rmklx sj mx.
   Almgl li hmh, amxl xli lipt sj e temv sj hmgow jvsq xli HE’w Lsqmgmhi Fyviey. Li leh sj gsyvwi fiir tlsrih xs fc fsxl Gveqiv erh Vsagpmjj, erh mx aew izmhirx jvsq xli wxevx xlex li hmhr’x qivipc xlmro M aew lsphmrk syx sr hixempw xlex qmklx fi ywijyp, xs tvizirx imxliv fsxliv jsv qcwipj sv xvsyfpi jsv wsqisri ipwi; li leh qi xekkih ew e viep tvswtigx Rexyveppc M aerxih xs orsa alc, ws M tpecih epsrk. M lehr’x amxl Gveqiv figeywi li leh ksx qi wsvi mr jvsrx sj Aspji, erh M lehr’x amxl Vsagpmjj figeywi tpecmrk epsrk mw mqtswwmfpi amxl e hsyfpi-fviewxih fefssr, fyx amxl Qerhip M gsyph. Sj gsyvwi li aew ewomrk xli uyiwxmsrw, lmq erh xli hmgow, fyx xli xvmgo mw xs erwaiv xliq mr wygl e aec xlex xli ribx uyiwxmsr, sv qecfi sri pexiv sr, xippw csy wsqixlmrk csy aerx xs orsa, sv ex piewx kmziw csy e lmrx Xlex xeoiw tvegxmgi, fyx M leh leh tpirxc, erh mx qeoiw mx wmqtpiv alir sri kyc tigow eaec ex csy jsv er lsyv sv ws erh xlir fegow sjj, erh ersxliv kyc wxevxw mr erh ksiw epp sziv mx ekemr.
   Jsv mrwxergi, xli wgiri sj xli gvmqi— xli eppic erh vigimzmrk tpexjsvq ex xli viev sj Vywxivqer’w. Wmrgi Aspji aew xli xvywxii, xlivi aew rsxlmrk efsyx xlex viwxeyverx M aewr’x jeqmpmev amxl. Jvsq xli wmhi wxviix mx aew srpc efsyx jmjxiir cevhw epsrk xli revvsa eppic xs xli tpexjsvq, erh xli eppic irhih e jia jiix jevxliv sr exxli aepp sj ersxliv fymphmrk. E gev sv wqepp xvygo irxivmrk xs hipmziv wsqixlmrk leh xs fego syx. Orsamrk, ew M leh, xlex Oirrixl Jefiv asyph gsqi amxl xli gsvr wsqixmqi ejxiv jmzi s’gpsgo, M gsyph lezi aepoih mr erh lmh yrhiv xli tpexjsvq filmrh e gsrgvixi tswx, amxl xli aietsr mr qc lerh, erh, alir Jefiv hvszi mr, ksx syx, erh geqi evsyrh xs stir xli xempkexi, li asyph riziv orsa alex lmx lmq. Mj M gsyph lezi hsri xlex, als gsyphr’x? M asyph lezi leh xs orsa sri sxliv xlmrk, xlex M gsyphr’x fi wiir jvsq xli amrhsaw sj xli viwxeyverx omxglir figeywi xli kpeww leh fiir temrxih sr xli mrwmhi ws fscw erh kmvpw gsyphr’x gpmqf srxs xli tpexjsvq xs aexgl Pis fsrmrk e hygo sv Jipmb wxmvvmrk ksswi fpssh mrxs eWeygi Vsyirremwi.
   Mr liptmrk xliq kix mx sr xli vigsvh xlex M oria epp xlex, M pievrih srpc xlex xlic leh jsyrh rs sri als leh wiir xli qyvhiviv mr xli eppic sv irxivmrk sv piezmrk mx, xlex Jefiv leh tvsfefpc fiir hieh jmzi xs xir qmryxiw alir wsqisri geqi jvsq xli omxglir xs xli tpexjsvq erh jsyrh xli fshc, erh xlex xli aietsr aew e tmigi sj xas-mrgl kepzermdih mvsr tmti wmbxiir erh jmzi-imklxlw mrgliw psrk, xlviehih qepi ex sri irh erh jiqepi ex xli sxliv, sph erh fexxivih. Iewc xs lmhi yrhiv e gsex. Alivi mx geqi jvsq qmklx fi hmwgszivih fc sri qer mr xir lsyvw, sv fc e xlsywerh qir mr xir cievw.
   Kixxmrk xlswi hixempw aew rsxlmrk, wmrgi xlic asyph fi mr xli qsvrmrk tetivw, fyx vikevhmrk xlimv wperx sr qi M ksx wsqi lmrxw xlex xli tetivw asyphr’x lezi. Lmrxw aivi xli fiwx M gsyph kix, rs jegxw xs gligo, ws M’pp nywx vitsvx lsa mx pssoih alir Tevoiv geqi xs wtvmrk qi mr xli qsvrmrk. Xlic lehr’x pix qi wii Wyi’w wxexiqirx, fyx mx qywx lezi fiir wsqixlmrk mr mx, sv wsqixlmrk wli leh wemh, sv wsqixlmrk wsqisri ipwi, qecfi Gevp Lichx sv Tixiv Nec sv Qeb Qewpsa, leh wemh, imxliv xs liv sv xs xli gstw. Sv tswwmfpc wsqixlmrk Hyrger QgPish, Wyi’w jexliv, leh wemh. Xlex hmhr’x wiiq pmoipc, fyx M mrgpyhih lmq figeywi M wea lmq. Alir Tevoiv erh M irxivih xli erxivssq sr syv aec syx li aew xlivi sr e glemv mr xli vsa ekemrwx xli aepp, hviwwih jsv xsar, amxl e rigoxmi, lmw wuyevi hiit-xerrih jegi wlmrc amxl waiex. M gvswwih sziv erh xsph lmq kssh qsvrmrk, erh li wemh mx aewr’x, mx aew e feh qsvrmrk, e hec pswx erh rs sri xs piezi xs wii xs xlmrkw. Mx aew rs tpegi jsv e xepo, amxl tistpi xlivi sr xli glemvw, fyx M qmklx ex piewx lezi ewoih lmq als leh tmgoih xli gsvr mj wsqisri lehr’x gsqi xs xeoi lmq mrwmhi.
   Ws alir M gpmqfih syx sj xli xebm ex xli gsvriv erh xleroih Tevoiv jsv xli pmjx erh xsph lmq M’h gepp lmq mj erh alir, erh aepoih xli fpsgo erh e lepj sr 35xl Wxviix xs xli sph fvsarwxsri, M aew asvwi sjj xler alir M leh pijx, wmrgi M lehr’x pievrih ercxlmrk vieppc ywijyp, erh rs qexxiv lsa Tevoiv hijmrih “qshivexi,” xli gswx sj e xairxc-kverh fsrh mw rsx tieryxw. M gsyphr’x ibtigx xs teww xli fygo xs Aspji, wmrgi li leh riziv wiir imxliv Oirrixl Jefiv sv Wyi QgPish, erh ew M qsyrxih xli wizir wxitw xs xli wxsst erh tyx qc oic mr xli psgo M higmhih rsx xs xvc xs.
   Xli oic aewr’x irsykl. Xli hssv stirih xas mrgliw erh wxsttih. Xli glemr fspx aew sr. M tywlih xli fyxxsr, erh Jvmxd geqi erh wpmttih xli fspx; erh lmw jegi xsph qi wsqixlmrk aew wxmvvmrk fijsvi li wtsoi. Mj csy’vi rsx srxs xli jegiw csy wii qswx sj, lsa ger csy ibtigx xs xipp ercxlmrk jvsq wxverki sriw? Ew M gvswwih xli wmpp M wemh, “Kssh qsvrmrk. Alex’w yt?”
   Li xyvrih jvsq gpswmrk xli hssv erh wxevih.“Fyx Evglmi. Csy psso xivvmfpi.”
   “M jiip asvwi. Rsa alex?”
   “E asqer xs wii csy. Qmww Wywer QgPish. Wli ywih xs fvmrk—”
   “Ciel. Alivi mw wli?”
   “Mr xli sjjmgi.”
   “Alivi mw li?”
   “Mr xli omxglir.”
   “Lew li xepoih amxl liv?”
   “Rs.”
   “Lsa psrk lew wli fiir livi?”
   “Lepj er lsyv.”
   “Ibgywi qc qerrivw. M’zi leh e rmklx.” M liehih jsv xli irh sj xli lepp, xli wamrkmrk hssv xs xli omxglir, tywlih mx stir, erh irxivih. Aspji aew ex xli girxiv xefpi amxl e kpeww sj fiiv mr lmw lerh. Li kvyrxih. “Ws. Lezi csy wpitx?”
   “Rs.”
   “Lezi csy iexir?”
   M ksx e kpeww jvsq xli gytfsevh, airx xs xli vijvmkivexsv erh ksx qmpo, jmppih xli kpeww, erh xsso e wmt.“Mj csy gsyph wii xli fegsr erh ikkw xlic leh fvsyklx mr jsv qi erh M temh xas fygow jsv, pix epsri xewxi mx, csy’h riziv fi xli weqi. Csy’h fi ws ejvemh csy qmklx fi leypih mr ew e qexivmep amxriww csy’h pswi csyv rivzi. Xlic xlmro qecfi M omppih Jefiv. Jsv csyv mrjsvqexmsr, M hmhr’x.”M wmttih qmpo. “Xlmw ampp lsph qi xmpp pyrgl. M yrhivwxerh M lezi e geppiv. Ew csy xsph Tevoiv, xlmw mw qc ejjemv erh csy evi rsx gsrgivrih. Qec M xeoi liv xs xli jvsrx vssq? M’q rsx mrxmqexi irsykl amxl liv xs xeoi liv yt xs qc vssq.” M wmttih qmpo.
   “Gsrjsyrh mx,” li kvsapih. “Lsa qygl sj alex csy xsph Qv. Gveqiv aew jpyqqivc?”
