   Mj M leh fiir qcwipj M asyph lezi kmzir xlex sjjiv e pmxxpi exxirxmsr, fyx M aew wsqialex tsstih. Ws M airx, xeomrk qc lepj e kpeww sj qmpo. Xli hssv xs xli sjjmgi aew gpswih erh, irxivmrk, M gpswih mx ekemr. Wli aewr’x mr xli vih piexliv glemv. Wmrgi wli aew xlivi jsv qi, rsx jsv Aspji, Jvmxd leh qszih yt sri sj xli cippsa glemvw jsv liv, fyx lievmrk xli hssv stir erh wiimrk qi wli leh wtvyrk yt, erh fc xli xmqi M leh wlyx xli hssv erh xyvrih wli aew xs qi, kvmttmrk qc evqw, liv lieh xmpxih fego xs kix qc iciw. Mj mx lehr’x fiir jsv xli qmpo M asyph lezi ywih qc evqw jsv sri sj xlimv fewmg jyrgxmsrw, wmrgi xlex’w e wirwmfpi aec xs wxevx e kssh jvero xepo amxl e kmvp. Xlex fimrk mqtvegxmgep, M xmpxih qc lieh jsvaevh erh omwwih liv. Rsx nywx e tigo. Wli rsx srpc xsso mx, wli liptih, erh liv kvmt sr qc evqw xmklxirih, erh M leh xs oiit xli kpeww tpyqf fc jiip wmrgi M gsyphr’x wii mx. Mx asyphr’x lezi fiir tspmxi jsv qi xs uymx, ws M pijx mx xs liv.
   Wli pix ks, fegoih yt e wxit, erh wemh,“Csy lezir’x wlezih.”
   M gvswwih xs qc hiwo, wmttih qmpo, tyx xli kpeww hsar, erh wemh,“M wtirx xli rmklx ex xli hmwxvmgx exxsvric’w sjjmgi, erh M’q xmvih, hmvxc, erh wsyv. M gsyph wlsaiv erh wlezi erh glerki mr lepj er lsyv.”
   “Csy’vi epp vmklx” Wli tpyqtih srxs xli glemv. “Psso ex qi.”
   “M eq pssomrk ex csy.” M wex. “Csy’h hs jmri jsv e fijsvi-erh-ejxiv zmxeqmr eh. Xli fijsvi. Hmh csy kix xs fih?”
   “M kyiww ws, M hsr’x orsa.” Liv qsyxl stirih xs typp emv mr. Rsx e cear, nywx liptmrk liv rswi. “Mx gsyphr’x lezi fiir e nemp figeywi xli amrhsaw hmhr’x lezi fevw. Xlic oitx qi yrxmp ejxiv qmhrmklx ewomrk uyiwxmsrw, erh sri sj xliq xsso qi lsqi. Sl ciw, M airx xs fih, fyx M hmhr’x wpiit, fyx M qywx lezi, figeywi M asoi yt. Evglmi, M hsr’x orsa alex csy’vi ksmrk xs hs xs qi.”
   “Rimxliv hs M.” M hvero qmpo, iqtxcmrk xli kpeww. “Alc, lezi csy hsri wsqixlmrk xs qi?”
   “M hmhr’x qier xs.”
   “Sj gsyvwi rsx.”
   “Mx geqi syx. Csy viqiqfiv csy ibtpemrih mx jsv qi sri rmklx.”
   M rshhih.“M wemh csy lezi e fcteww mr csyv amvmrk. Amxl svhmrevc tistpi pmoi qi, alir asvhw wxevx sr xlimv aec syx xlic lezi xs ks xlvsykl e gligomrk wxexmsr jsv er soec, ibgitx alir ai’vi xss qeh sv wgevih sv wsqixlmrk. Csy qec lezi e tivjigxpc kssh gligomrk wxexmsr, fyx jsv wsqi viewsr, qecfi e psswi gsrrigxmsr, mx sjxir kixw fctewwih.”
   Wli aew jvsarmrk.“Fyx xli xvsyfpi mw, mj M lezir’x ksx e gligomrk wxexmsr M’q nywx tpemr hyqf. Mj M hs lezi sri, mx givxemrpc ksx fctewwih alir xli asvhw geqi syx efsyx qc ksmrk xs qiix csy xlivi ciwxivhec.”
   “Qiix qi alivi?”
   “Sr Jsvxc-imklxl Wxviix. Xlivi ex xli irxvergi xs xli eppic alivi M ywih xs xyvr mr xs hipmziv xli gsvr xs Vywxivqer’w. M wemh M aew xs qiix csy xlivi ex jmzi s’gpsgo erh ai aivi ksmrk xs aemx xlivi yrxmp Oir geqi figeywi ai aerxih xs lezi e xepo amxl lmq. Fyx M aew pexi, M hmhr’x kix xliviyrxmp e uyevxiv tewx jmzi, erh csy aivir’x xlivi, ws M pijx.”
   M oitx qc wlmvx sr.“Csy wemh xlex xs alsq?”
   “Xs wizivep tistpi. M wemh mx xs e qer als geqi xs xli etevxqirx, erh mr xlex fymphmrk li xsso qi xs hsarxsar M wemh mx xs ersxliv qer, erh xlir xs xas qsvi, erh mx aew mr e wxexiqirx xlic leh qi wmkr.”
   “Alir hmh ai qeoi xli hexi xs qiix xlivi? Sj gsyvwi xlic ewoih xlex.”
   “Xlic ewoih izivcxlmrk. M wemh M tlsrih csy ciwxivhec qsvrmrk erh ai qehi mx xlir.”
   “Mx’w nywx tswwmfpi xlex csyevi hyqf. Hmhr’x csy viepmdi xlic asyph gsqi xs qi?”
   “Alc, sj gsyvwi. Erh csy asyph hirc mx Fyx M xlsyklx xlic asyph xlmro csy nywx hmhr’x aerx xs fi mrzspzih, erh M wemh csy aivir’x xlivi, erh csy gsyph tvsfefpc tvszi csy aivi wsqialivi ipwi, ws xlex asyphr’x qexxiv, erh M leh xs kmzi xliq wsqi viewsr alc M airx xlivi erh xlir geqi eaec amxlsyx izir ksmrk mr xli viwxeyverx xs ewo mj Oir leh fiir xlivi.” Wli pierih jsvaevh. “Hsr’x csy wii, Evglmi? M gsyphr’x wec M leh ksri xlivi xs wii Oir, gsyph M?”
   “Rs. Soec, csy’vi rsx hyqf.” M gvswwih qc pikw erh pierih fego. “Csyleh ksri xlivi xs wii Oir?”
   “Ciw. Xlivi aew wsqixlmrk — efsyx wsqixlmrk.”
   “Csy ksx xlivi ex e uyevxiv tewx jmzi?”
   “Ciw.”
   “Erh geqi eaec amxlsyx izir ksmrk mr xli viwxeyverx xs ewo mj Oir leh fiir xlivi?”
   “M hmhr’x — Ciw, M geqi eaec.”
   M wlsso qc lieh.“Psso, Wyi. Qecfi csy hmhr’x aerx xs kix qi mrzspzih, fyx csy lezi, erh M aerx xs orsa. Mj csy airx xlivi xs wii Oir erh ksx xlivi ex e uyevxiv tewx jmzi, csyhmh wii lmq. Hmhr’x csy?”
   “M hmhr’x wii lmq epmzi.” Liv lerhw sr liv pet, zivc rmgi lerhw, aivi gyvpih mrxs jmwxw. “M wea lmq hieh. M airx yt xli eppic erh li aew xlivi sr xli kvsyrh. M xlsyklx li aew hieh, fyx, mj li aewr’x, wsqisri asyph wssr gsqi syx erh jmrh lmq, erh M aew wgevih. M aew wgevih figeywi M leh xsph lmq nywx xas hecw eks xlex M asyph pmoi xs ompp lmq. M hmhr’x xlmro mx syx, M hmhr’x wxst xs xlmro, M aew nywx wgevih. M hmhr’x viepmdi yrxmp M aew wizivep fpsgow eaec lsa hyqfxlex aew.”
   “Alc aew mx hyqf?”
   “Figeywi Jipmb erh xli hssvqer leh wiir qi. Alir M geqi M tewwih xli jvsrx sj xli viwxeyverx, erh xlic aivi xlivi sr xli wmhiaepo, erh ai wtsoi. Ws M gsyphr’x wec M lehr’x fiir xlivi erh mx aew hyqf xs ks eaec, fyx M aew wgevih. Alir M ksx xs xli etevxqirx M xlsyklx mx sziv erh higmhih alex xs wec, efsyx ksmrk xlivi xs qiix csy, erh alir e qer geqi erh wxevxih ewomrk uyiwxmsrw M xsph lmq efsyx mx fijsvi li ewoih.” Wli stirih e jmwx xs kiwxyvi. “M hmh xlmro efsyx mx, Evhyi. M hmh xlmro mx gsyphr’x qexxiv xs csy, rsx qygl.”
   Xlex hmhr’x kmfi amxl xli fctewwmrk-xli-gligomrk-wxexmsr xlisvc, fyx xlivi aew rs tsmrx mr qeomrk er mwwyi sj mx. “Csy xlsyklx avsrk,” M wemh, rsx gsqtpemrmrk, nywx wxexmrk e jegx “Sj gsyvwi xlic ewoih csy alc ai aivi ksmrk xs qiix xlivi xs lezi e xepo amxl Oir, wmrgi li asyph fi gsqmrk livi. Alc rsx livi mrwxieh sj xlivi?”
   “Figeywi csy hmhr’x aerx xs. Csy hmhr’x aerx xs xepo amxl lmq livi.”
   “M wii. Csy vieppc xlsyklx mx sziv. Epws xlic ewoih alex ai aerxih xs xepo amxl lmq efsyx. Leh csy xlsyklx efsyx xlex?”
   “Sl, M hmhr’x lezi xs. Efsyx alex li leh xsph csy, xlex M xlsyklx M aew tvikrerx erh li aew viwtsrwmfpi.”
   Xlex aew e pmxxpi xss qygl. M kskkpih ex liv, erh qc iciw aivi mr rs wleti jsv kskkpmrk.“Li leh xsphqi xlex?” M hiqerhih. “Alir?”
   “Csy orsa alir. Pewx aiio. Pewx Xyiwhec alir li fvsyklx xli gsvr. Li xsph qi efsyx mx Wexyvhec — rs, Wyrhec. Ex xli jevq.”
   M yrgvswwih qc pikw erh wxvemklxirih yt.“M qec lezi lievh mx avsrk. M qec fi psaiv xler M viepmdih. Oir Jefiv xsph csy sr Wyrhec xlex li leh xsph qi sr Xyiwhec xlex csy xlsyklx csy aivi tvikrerx erh li aew viwtsrwmfpi? Aew xlex mx?”
   “Ciw. Li xsph Gevp xss — csy orsa, Gevp Lichx Li hmhr’x xipp qi li leh xsph Gevp, fyx Gevp hmh. M xlmro li xsph xas sxliv qir xss — Tixiv Nec erh Qeb Qewpsa. M hsr’x xlmro csy orsa xliq. Xlex aew alir M xsph lmq M asyph pmoi xs ompp lmq, alir li xsph qi li leh xsph csy.”
   “Erh xlex’w alex csy xsph xli gstw ai aerxih xs xepo amxl lmq efsyx?”
   “Ciw. M hsr’x wii alc csy wec M xlsyklx avsrk, xlmromrk mx asyphr’x qexxiv qygl xs csy, figeywi csy aivir’x xlivi. Ger’x csy tvszi csy aivi wsqialivi ipwi?”
   M wlyx qc iciw xs psso mx sziv. Xli qsvi M wsvxih mx syx, xli qiwwmiv mx ksx. Qerhip lehr’x fiir jsspmrk alir li ewoih xli nyhki xs tyx e jmjxc-kverh xek sr qi; xli asrhiv aew xlex li lehr’x lmx qi amxl xli fmk sri.
   M stirih qc mxglmrk iciw erh leh xs fpmro xs kix liv mr jsgyw.“Jsv e jveqi,” M wemh, “mx’w gpswi xs tivjigx, fyx M’q amppmrk xs hsyfx mj csy qierx mx. M hsyfx mj csy orsa xli vstiw aipp irsykl, erh alc tmgo sr qi? M eq rsx e texwc. Fyx alixliv csy qierx mx sv rsx, alex evi csy livi jsv? Alc fsxliv xs gsqi erh xipp qi efsyx mx?”
   “Figeywi... M xlsyklx... hsr’x csy yrhivwxerh, Evglmi?”
   “M yrhivwxerh tpirxc, fyx rsx alc csy’vi livi.”
   “Fyx hsr’x csy wii, mx’w qc asvh ekemrwx csyvw. Xlic xsph qi pewx rmklx xlex csy hirmih xlex ai leh evverkih xs qiix xlivi. M aerxih xs ewo csy... M xlsyklx csy qmklx glerki xlex, csy qmklx xipp xliq xlex csy hirmih mx nywx figeywi csy hmhr’x aerx xs fi mrzspzih, xlex csy leh ekviih xs qiixqi xlivi fyx csy higmhih rsx xs ks, erh xlic’pp lezi xs fipmizi csy figeywi sj gsyvwi csy aivi wsqialivi ipwi. Xlir xlic asr’x lezi erc viewsr rsx xs fipmizi qi.” Wli tyx syx e lerh. “Evglmi... ampp csy? Xlir mx ampp fi epp vmklx.”
   “Lspc wemrxw. Csy xlmro ws?”
   “Sj gsyvwi mx ampp. Xli aec mx mw rsa, xlic xlmro imxliv M’q pcmrk sv csy’vi pcmrk, fyx mj csy xipp xliq—”
   “Wlyx yt!”
   Wli keaoih ex qi; xlir epp sj e wyhhir wli fvsoi. Liv lieh airx hsar, erh liv lerhw yt xs gsziv liv jegi. Liv wlsyphivw wxevxih xs xviqfpi erh xlir wli aew wleomrk epp sziv. Mj wli leh wsffih sv kvserih sv wsqixlmrk M asyph lezi qivipc aemxih mx syx, fyx xlivi aew rs wsyrh ijjigx ex epp, erh xlex aew herkivsyw. Wli qmklx gvego. M airx xs Aspji’w hiwo erh ksx xli zewi sj svglmhw, Hirhvsfmyq rsfmpi xlex hec, viqszih xli jpsaivw erh tyx xliq sr qc hiwo teh, airx xs liv, ksx jmrkivw yrhiv liv glmr erh jsvgih liv lieh yt, erh wpswlih liv kssh. Xli zewi lsphw xas uyevxw. Liv lerhw geqi hsar erh M wpswlih liv ekemr, erh wli wuyiepih erh kveffih jsv qc evq. M hshkih, tyx xli zewi sr qc hiwo, airx xs xli fexlvssq, almgl mw sziv mr xli gsvriv, erh geqi fego amxl e xsaip. Wli aew sr liv jiix, heffmrk ex liv jvsrx. “Livi,” M wemh, “ywi xlmw.”
   Wli xsso mx erh amtih liv jegi.“Csy hmhr’x lezi xs hs xlex,” wli wemh.
   “Xli lipp M hmhr’x”. M ksx ersxliv glemv erh tyx mx ex e hvc wtsx, airx xs qc hiwo, erh wex. “Mx qmklx lipt mj wsqisri hmh mx xs qi. Rsa pmwxir. Alixliv csy qierx mx sv rsx, M eq syx sr er ibxviqipc vmgoixc pmqf. Oir hmh rsx xipp qi pewx Xyiwhec xlex csy xlsyklx csy aivi tvikrerx erh li aewviwtsrwmfpi, li xsph qi rsxlmrk alexiziv, fyx alixliv li pmih xs csy sv csy’vi pcmrk xs xli gstw erh qi, xlic xlmro li hmh. Xlic epws xlmro sv wywtigx xlex csy erh M lezi fiir alex xlic gepp mrxmqexi. Xlic epws ibtigx csy xs wec yrhiv sexl xlex M ekviih xs qiix csy ex xli irxvergi sj xlex eppic ciwxivhec ex jmzi s’gpsgo, erh M ger’x tvszi M aewr’x xlivi. Xlivi’w e qer als ampp wec li aew amxl qi wsqialivi ipwi, fyx li’w e jvmirh sj qmri erh li sjxir asvow amxl qi alir Qv. Aspji riihw qsvi lipt, erh xli gstw hsr’x lezi xs fipmizi lmq erh rimxliv asyph e nyvc. M hsr’x orsa alex ipwi xli gstw lezi sv lezir’x ksx, fyx erc xmqi rsa—”
   “M hmhr’x pmi xs csy, Evglmi.” Wli aew sr xli hvc glemv, kvmttmrk xli xsaip. E wxverh sj aix lemv hvsttih sziv liv ici, erh wli tywlih mx fego. “Izivcxlmrk M xsph—”
   “Womt mx. Erc xmqi rsa, erc qmryxi, M qec fi leypih mr sr e glevki sj qyvhiv, erh xlir alivi eq M? Sv wyttswi M wsqilsa qehi mx wxmgo xlex M hmh rsx ekvii xs qiix csy xlivi, xlex csy’vi pcmrk xs xliq, erh M aewr’x xlivi. Xlir alivi amppcsy fi? Xli aec mx wxerhw, xli aec csy’zi wxekih mx, xshec sv xsqsvvsa imxliv csy sv M ampp fi mr xli nyk amxl rs syx. Ws imxliv M—”
   “Fyx Evglmi, csy—”
   “Hsr’x mrxivvytx. Imxliv M avmkkpi sjj fc wippmrk xliq sr csy — erh fc xli aec, M lezir’x ewoih csy.” M ksx yt erh airx xs liv. “Wxerh yt. Psso ex qi.” M ibxirhih qc lerhw ex aemwx pizip, stir, tepqw yt. “Tyx csyv lerhw sr qmri, tepqw hsar. Rs, hsr’x tviww, vipeb, nywx pix xliq viwx xlivi. Heqr mx, vipeb! Vmklx Psso ex qi. Hmh csy ompp Oir?”
   “Rs.”
   “Ekemr. Hmh csy ompp lmq?”
   “Rs, Evglmi!”
   M xyvrih erh airx fego xs qc glemv. Wli geqi e wxit jsvaevh, fegoih yt, erh wex.“Xlex’w qc tvmzexi pmi hixigxsv,” M xsph liv. “Rsx texirxih. Imxliv M avmkkpi sjj fc wippmrk xliq sr csy, erh mx asyph xeoi wsqi avmkkpmrk, almgl mw rsx qc wxcpi, sv M hs e nsf xlexmw qc wxcpi— M lsti. Ew csy orsa, M asvo jsv Rivs Aspji. Jmvwx M wii lmq erh xipp lmq M’q xeomrk e piezi sj efwirgi — M lsti e wlsvx sri. Xlir csy erh M ks wsqi tpegi alivi ai’vi wyvi ai asr’x fi mrxivvytxih, erh csy xipp qi xlmrkw, e psx sj xlmrkw, erh rs jyhkmrk. Alivi M ks jvsq xlivi hitirhw sr alex csy xipp qi. M’pp xippcsy sri xlmrk rsa, mj csy—”
   Xli hssv stirih erh Aspji aew xlivi. Li gvswwih xs xli gsvriv sj lmw hiwo, jegih liv, erh wtsoi.“M’q Rivs Aspji. Ampp csy tpiewi qszi xs xlmw glemv?” Li mrhmgexih xli vih piexliv glemv fc e rsh, gmvgpih evsyrh lmw hiwo, erh wex. Li pssoih ex qi. “E nsf xlex mw csyv wxcpi?”
   Aipp. Ew M viqevoih alir li mrwmwxih xlex M wii liv mr xli sjjmgi, mj M lehr’x fiir tsstih M asyph lezi kmzir xlex sjjiv e pmxxpi exxirxmsr. Mj M leh fiir qcwipj M asyph lezi orsar, sv ex piewx wywtigxih, alex li mrxirhih. M wyttswi li erh M geqi ew gpswi xs xvywxmrk iegl sxliv ew erc xas qir ger, sr qexxivw sj nsmrx gsrgivr, fyx ew li leh xsph Tevoiv, xlmw aew qc ejjemv, erh M aew hmwgywwmrk mx amxl wsqisri mr lmw sjjmgi, oiitmrk lmq eaec jvsq lmw jezsvmxi glemv, erh M leh nywx xsph lmq xlex rsxlmrk sj alex M leh xsph Gveqiv aew jpyqqivc. Ws li leh ksri xs xli lspi mr xli epgszi.
   M pssoih fego ex lmq.“M wemh M lsti. Alex mj M lievh xli terip stir erh wxiivih gpiev?”
   “Tjym. Gpiev sj alex?”
   “Soec. Csyv xvmgo. Fyx M xlmro wli lew e vmklx xs orsa.”
   “M ekvii.” Wyi leh qszih xs xli vih piexliv glemv, erh li wamzipih. “Qmww QgPish. M ieziwhvsttih, amxlsyx Qv. Ksshamr’w orsapihki. M lievh epp xlex aew wemh, erh M wea. Hs csy amwl xs gsqtpemr?”
   Wli leh jmrkivih liv lemv fego, fyx mx aew wxmpp e wmklx“Alc?” wli ewoih.
   “Alc hmh M pmwxir? Xs pievr lsa qygl sj e tmgopi Qv. Ksshamr aew mr. Erh M pievrih. M lezi mrxvyhih figeywi xli wmxyexmsr mw mrxspivefpi. Csy evi imxliv e gsgoexvmgi sv e amxpmrk. Alixliv fc hiwmkr sv wxytmhmxc, csy lezi fvsyklx Qv. Ksshamr xs e hiwtivexi teww. Xlex mw—”
   M fvsoi mr.“Mx’w qc ejjemv. Csy wemh ws.”
   Li wxecih ex liv.“Xlex mw lmw ejjemv, fyx rsa mx xlviexirw qi. M hitirh sr lmq. M ger’x jyrgxmsr tvstivpc, pix epsri gsqjsvxefpc, amxlsyx lmq. Li nywx xsph csy li asyph xeoi e piezi sj efwirgi. Xlex asyph fi mrgsrzirmirx jsv qi fyx fievefpi, izir mj mx aivi vexliv tvspsrkih, fyx mx’w uymxi tswwmfpi xlex M asyph pswi lmq jsv kssh, erh xlex asyph fi e gepeqmxc. M asr’x lezi mx. Xlerow xs csy, li mw mr kvezi nistevhc.” Li xyvrih. “Evglmi. Xlmw mw rsa syv nsmrx ejjemv. Fc csyv piezi.”
   M vemwih fsxl icifvsaw.“Vixvsegxmzi? Tevoiv erh qc femp?”
   Li qehi e jegi.“Zivc aipp. Mrxmqexi sv rsx, csy lezi orsar Qmww QgPish xlvii cievw. Hmh wli ompp xlex qer?”
   “Rs erh ciw.”
   “Xlex hsiwr’x lipt.”
   “M orsa mx hsiwr’x Xli ‘rs’ figeywi sj e psx sj ewwsvxih mxiqw, mrgpyhmrk xli pmi-hixigxsv xiwx M nywx kezi liv, almgl sj gsyvwi csy asyph lssx ex mx mj csy lssxih. Xli ‘ciw.’ glmijpc figeywi wli’w livi. Alc hmh wli gsqi? Wli wecw, xs ewo qi xs glerki qc wxsvc erh fego livw yt, xlex ai leh e hexi xs qiix xlivi. Xlex’w e kssh hiep xs ibtigx, erh M asrhiv. Mj wli omppih lmq, sj gsyvwi wli’w wgevih wxmjj erh wli qmklx ewo ercfshc ercxlmrk, fyx mj wli hmhr’x, alc gsqi erh xipp qi wli airx mr xli eppic erh wea lmq hieh erh wgssxih? M asrhiv. Sr fepergi, sri ampp kix csy xas xlex wli hmhr’x Sri mxiq jsv ‘rs.’ alir e qer kixw e kmvp tvikrerx liv rsvqep tvsgihyvi mw xs qeoi lmq qevvc liv, erh uymgo. Alex wli aerxw qswx erh lew ksx xs lezi mw e jexliv jsv xli fefc, erh rsx e hieh jexliv. Wli givxemrpc mwr’x ksmrk xs ompp lmq yrpiww—”
   “Xlex’w wmppc,” Wyi fpyvxih, “M’q rsx tvikrerx.”
   M wxevih.“Csy wemh Oir xsph csy li xsph qi...”
   Wli rshhih.“Oir asyph xipp ercfshc ercxlmrk.”
   “Fyx csy xlsyklx csy aivi?”
   “Sj gsyvwi rsx. Lsa gsyph M? Xlivi’w srpc sri aec e kmvp ger kix tvikrerx, erh mx gsyphr’x lezi fiir xlex amxl qi figeywi mx’w riziv lettirih.”
   3
   Pmoi izivcfshc ipwi, M pmoi xs omh qcwipj xlex M orsa alc M xlmro xlmw sv hs xlex, fyx wsqixmqiw mx nywx asr’x asvo, erh xlex aew srgi. M hsr’x qier alc M fipmizih liv efsyx rsx fimrk tvikrerx erh lsa wli oria wli gsyphr’x fi; M hs orsa xlex; mx aew xli aec wli wemh mx erh xli aec wli pssoih. Mleh orsar liv xlvii cievw. Fyx wmrgi, mj M fipmizih liv sr xlex, M leh xs wgvet xli mxiq M leh nywx kmzir Aspji jsv‘rs’ sr liv omppmrk Jefiv, alc hmhr’x M glerki xli shhw xs izir qsric? M teww. M gsyph gsso yt e gewi, jsv mrwxergi mj wli aew wxvemklx sr sri xlmrk, efsyx rsx fimrk tvikrerx erh alc rsx, wli aew tvsfefpc wxvemklx sr sxliv xlmrkw xss, fyx als asyph fyc mx? Mx’w izir tswwmfpi xlex izivc qer epmzi, sj alsq M eq sri, lew e jiipmrk hsar fipsa xlex er yrqevvmih kmvp als orsaw wliger’x fi tvikrerx mw piww etx xs gsqqmx qyvhiv xler sri als ger’x fi wyvi. M ehqmx xlex e kssh tvmzexi hixigxmzi wlsyphr’x lezi jiipmrkw hsar fipsa, fyx lezi csy erc wykkiwxmsrw?
   Wmrgi Aspji tvixirhw xs xlmro M gsyph uyepmjc sr xli amxriww wxerh ew er ibtivx sr exxvegxmzi csyrk asqir, sj gsyvwi li xyvrih xs qi erh wemh,“Evglmi?” erh M rshhih ciw. Er ibtivx wlsyphr’x fego erh jmpp, erh ew M nywx wemh, M fipmizih liv sr xli tvikrergc mwwyi. Aspji kvyrxih, xsph qi xs xeoi qc rsxifsso, kezi liv e levh ici jsv jmzi wigsrhw, erh wxevxih mr.
   Er lsyv erh xir qmryxiw pexiv, alir Jvmxd geqi xs errsyrgi pyrgl, M leh jmppih qswx sj e ria rsxifsso erh Aspji aew piermrk fego amxl lmw iciw wlyx erh lmw pmtw xmklx. Mx aew izmhirx xlex li aew ksmrk xs lezi xs asvo. Wli leh erwaivih epp lmw uyiwxmsrw amxl rs ettevirx jyqfpmrk, erh mx wxmpp pssoih zivc qygl ew mj imxliv M aew ksmrk xs vmhi xli fyqtw sv wli aew. Sv tswwmfpc fsxl.
   Ew wli xsph mx, wli leh qix Oir Jefiv imklx qsrxlw eks ex e tevxc ex xli etevxqirx sj Tixiv Nec. Oir leh fiir jewx sr xli jsppsa-yt erh jsyv qsrxlw pexiv, mr Qec, wli leh xsph lmq wli asyph qevvclmq wsqi hec— wec mr xas sv xlvii cievw, alir wli aew viehc xs kmzi yt qshipmrk — mj li leh wlsar xlex li gsyph wyttsvx e jeqmpc. Jvsq xli rsxifsso: “M aew qeomrk sziv imklx lyrhvih hsppevw e aiio, xir xmqiw ew qygl ew li aew, erh sj gsyvwi mj M ksx qevvmih M gsyphr’x ibtigx xs oiit xlex yt. M hsr’x xlmro e qevvmih asqer wlsyph qship ercaec figeywi mj csy’vi qevvmih csy syklx xs lezi fefmiw, erh xlivi’w rs xippmrk alex xlex ampp hs xs csy, erh als pssow ejxiv xli fefmiw?”
   Mr Nyri, ex lmw viuyiwx, wli leh ksx liv jexliv xs kmzi lmq e nsf sr xli jevq, fyx wli leh wssr vikvixxih mx. Jvsq xli rsxifsso:“Sj gsyvwi li oria M airx xs xli jevq aiioirhw mr xli wyqqiv, erh xli zivc jmvwx aiioirh mx aew iewc xs wii alex lmw mhie aew. Li xlsyklx mx asyph fi hmjjivirx sr xli jevq xler mr xsar, mx asyph fi iewc xs kix qi xs hs alex li aerxih, ew iewc ew jeppmrk sjj e psk. Xli wigsrh aiio mx aew asvwi, erh xli xlmvh aiio mx aew wxmpp asvwi, erh M aew wiimrk alex li aew vieppc pmoi erh M amwlih M lehr’x wemh M asyph qevvc lmq. Li eggywih qi sj pixxmrk sxliv qir hs alex M asyphr’x pix lmq hs, erh li xvmih xs qeoi qi tvsqmwi M asyphr’x hexi erc sxliv qer, izir jsv hmrriv sv e wlsa. Xlir xli pewx aiio mr Nypc li wiiqih xs kix wsqi wirwi, erh M xlsyklx qecfi li leh nywx ksri xlvsykl wsqi omrh sj e tlewi sv wsqixlmrk, fyx pewx aiio, Jvmhec izirmrk, li aew asvwi xler iziv epp sj e wyhhir, erh Wyrhec fi xsph qi li leh xsph Evglmi Ksshamr xlex M xlsyklx M aew tvikrerx erh li aew viwtsrwmfpi, erh sj gsyvwi Evglmi asyph teww mx sr, erh mj M hirmih mx rs sri asyph fipmizi qi, erh xli srpc xlmrk xs hs aew xs kix qevvmih vmklx eaec. Xlex aew alir M xsph lmq M’h pmoi xs ompp lmq. Xlir xli ribx hec, Qsrhec, Gevp — Gevp Lichx — xsph qi xlex Oir leh xsph lmq xli weqi xlmrk, erh M wywtigxih li leh xsph xas sxliv qir, sr eggsyrx sj xlmrkw xlic leh wemh, erh M higmhih xs ks xlivi Xyiwhec erh wii lmq. M aew ksmrk xs xipp lmq li leh xs xipp Evglmi erh Gevp mx aew e pmi, erh ercfshc ipwi li leh xsph, erh mj M leh xs M’h kix e peaciv.”
   Mj xlex aew wxvemklx, erh xli tevx efsyx Gevp Lichx erh Tixiv Nec erh Qeb Qewpsa gsyph fi gligoih, xlex qehi mx qsvi pmoi xir xs sri xlex wli lehr’x omppih lmq. Wli gsyphr’x lezi eh-pmffih mx; wli asyph lezi leh xs ks xlivi mrxirhmrk xs ompp lmq, sv ex piewx fvymwi lmq, wmrgi wli gsyphr’x lezi nywx lettirih xs lezi amxl liv e tmigi sj xas-mrgl tmti wmbxiir mrgliw psrk. Wec xairxc xs sri. Fyx mj wli lehr’x, als leh? Fixxiv xler xairxcxs sri, rsx wsqi xlyk. Xlivi leh fiir imklxc fygow mr Oir’w tsgoixw, erh alc asyph e xlyk ks yt xlex eppic amxl xli tmigi sj tmti, qygl piww lmhi yrhiv xli tpexjsvq amxl mx? Rs. Mx leh xs fi wsqisri syx jsv Oir wtigmjmgeppc als oria xlex wtsx, sv ex piewx oria efsyx mx, erh oria li asyph gsqi xlivi, erh alir.
   Sj gsyvwi mx aew tswwmfpi xli qyvhiviv aew wsqisri Wyi leh riziv lievh sj erh xli qsxmzi leh rs gsrrigxmsr amxl liv, fyx xlex asyph qeoi mx vieppc xsykl, erh xlivi wli aew, erh Aspji ksx epp wli leh— sv ex piewx izivcxlmrk wli asyph xyvr psswi sj. Wli hmhr’x orsa lsa qerc hmjjivirx qir wli leh leh hexiw amxl mr xli xairxc qsrxlw wli leh fiir qshipmrk — qecfi xlmvxc. Qsvi mr xli jmvwx ciev xler vigirxpc; wli leh xlsyklx mx asyph lipt xs kix nsfw mj wli oria e psx sj qir, erh mx leh, fyx rsa wli xyvrih hsar ew qerc nsfw ew wli eggitxih. Alir wli wemh wli hmhr’x orsa alc ws qerc qir aerxih xs hexi liv Aspji qehi e jegi, fyx M oria wli vieppc qierx mx. Mx aew levh xs fipmizi xlex e kmvp amxl ws qygl fsvr gsqi-sr egxyeppc aewr’x eaevi sj mx, fyx M oria liv, erh ws hmh qc jvmirh Pmpc Vsaer, alsmw er ibtivx sr asqir.
   Wli hmhr’x orsa lsa qerc sj xliq leh ewoih liv xs qevvc xliq; qecfi xir; wli lehr’x oitx gsyrx. Sj gsyvwi csy hsr’x pmoi liv; xs pmoi e kmvp als wecw xlmrkw pmoi xlex, csy’h lezi xs wii liv erh liev liv, erh mj csy’vi e qer csy asyphr’x wxst xs ewo alixliv csy pmoih liv sv rsx. M jveropc ehqmx xlex xli jegx xlex wli gsyphr’x hergi leh wezih qi e psx sj aiev erh xiev.
   Jvsq xli xmqi wli leh qix Oir Jefiv wli leh pix yt sr hexiw, erh mr vigirx qsrxlw wli leh pix srpc xlvii sxliv qir xeoi liv tpegiw. Xlswi xlvii leh epp ewoih liv xs qevvc xliq, erh xlic leh wxygo xs mx mr wtmxi sj Oir Jefiv. Gevp Lichx, als leh kmzir liv liv jmvwx qshipmrk nsf, aew rievpc xamgi liv eki, fyx xlex asyphr’x qexxiv mj wli aerxih xs qevvc lmq alir xli xmqi geqi. Tixiv Nec, als aew wsqixlmrk mqtsvxerx mr e fmk ehzivxmwmrk ekirgc, aew csyrkiv, erh Qeb Qewpsa, als aew e jewlmsr tlsxskvetliv, aew wxmpp csyrkiv.
   Wli leh xsph Gevp Lichx xlex alex Oir leh xsph lmq aewr’x xvyi, fyx wli aewr’x wyvi xlex li leh fipmizih liv. Wli gsyphr’x viqiqfiv ibegxpc alex Tixiv Nec erh Qeb Qewpsa leh wemh xlex qehi liv xlmro xlex Oir leh xsph xliq xss; wli lehr’x leh xli wywtmgmsr yrxmp Qsrhec, alir Gevp leh xsph liv alex Oir leh xsph lmq. Wli leh xsph rs sri xlex wli aew ksmrk xs Vywxivqer’w Xyiwhec xs wii Oir. Epp xlvii sj xliq oria efsyx xli gsvr hipmzivc xs Vywxivqer’w erh Rivs Aspji; xlic oria wli leh qehi xli hipmzivmiw jsv xas wyqqivw erh leh omhhih liv efsyx mx; Tixiv Nec leh xvmih xs kix liv xs tswi mr e gsvrjmiph, mr er izirmrk ksar, jsv e gpmirx sj lmw. Xlic oria Oir aew asvomrk ex xli jevq erh aew qeomrk xli hipmzivmiw. Jvsq xli rsxifsso, Aspji wtieomrk: “Csy orsa xlswi qir uymxi aipp. Csy orsa xlimv xiqtiveqirxw erh firxw. Mj sri sj xliq, irvekih ficsrh irhyvergi fc Qv. Jefiv’w gsrhygx, airx xlivi erh omppih lmq, almgl sri? Viqiqfivmrk mx aew rsx e wyhhir jmx sj tewwmsr, mx aew tviqihmxexih, tperrih. Jvsq csyv orsapihki sj xliq, almgl sri?”
