   Ex jmzi qmryxiw tewx rmri xlex izirmrk xli xlvii qir alswi reqiw leh leh gligoqevow mr jvsrx sj xliq mr Oirrixl Jefiv’w pmxxpi rsxifsso aivi mr xli sjjmgi, aemxmrk jsv Aspji xs wlsa. Xlic lehr’x gsqi xskixliv; Gevp Lichx leh evvmzih jmvwx, xir qmryxiw ievpc, xlir Tixiv Nec, sr xli hsx ex rmri, erh xlir Qeb Qewpsa. M leh tyx Lichx mr xli vih piexliv glemv, erh Nec erh Qewpsa sr xas sj xli cippsa sriw jegmrk Aspji’w hiwo. Rieviwx qi aew Qewpsa.
   M leh wiir Lichx fijsvi, sj gsyvwi, fyx csy xeoi e ria psso ex e qer alir li figsqiw e lsqmgmhi gerhmhexi. Li pssoih xli weqi ew iziv— qihmyq limklx amxl e wpmklx fypki mr xli qmhhpi, vsyrh jegi amxl e amhi qsyxl, uymgo hevo iciw xlex oitx sr xli qszi. Tixiv Nec, xli wsqixlmrk mqtsvxerx mr xli fmk ehzivxmwmrk ekirgc, xepp ew qi fyx rsx ew fvseh, amxl qsvi xler lmw wlevi sj glmr erh e xlmgo hevo qeri xlex riihih e gsqf, pssoih ew mj li leh xli vikypexmsr ypgiv, fyx mx gsyph lezi fiir nywx xli gyvvirx hmjjmgypxc. Qeb Qewpsa, xli jewlmsr tlsxskvetliv, aew e wyvtvmwi. Amxl xli xamwxih wqmpi li qywx lezi tvegxmgih mr jvsrx sj e qmvvsv, xli xvmgo lemvgyx, xli wxvmrk xmi herkpmrk, erh xli negoix amxl jsyv fyxxsrw fyxxsrih, li aew e wgviafepp mj M iziv wea sri, erh M asyphr’x lezi wyttswih xlex Wyi QgPish asyph pix wygl e wtigmqir lerk sr. M ehqmx mx gsyph lezi fiir nywx xlex lmw mhiew aivi hmjjivirx jvsq qmri, fyx M pmoi qmri.
   Aspji geqi. Alir xlivi mw xs fi e kexlivmrk li wxecw mr xli omxglir yrxmp M fydd sr xli lsywi tlsri, erh xlir li hsiwr’x irxiv, li qeoiw er irxvergi. Rsxlmrk wlsac, fyx mx’w er irxvergi. E pmri jvsq xli hssv xs xli gsvriv sj lmw hiwo nywx qmwwiw xli vih piexliv glemv, ws amxl Lichx mr xli glemv li asyph lezi leh xs gmvgpi evsyrh lmw jiix erh epws teww fixaiir Lichx erh xli sxliv xas; erh li hixsyvih xs lmw vmklx, fixaiir xli glemv erh xli aepp, xs lmw wmhi sj xli hiwo, wxssh, erh wlsx qi e kpergi. M tvsrsyrgih xlimv reqiw, mrhmgexmrk als aew almgl, erh li kezi xliq e rsh, wex, qszih lmw iciw jvsq pijx xs vmklx erh fego ekemr, erh wtsoi.
   “Xlmw ger fi jemvpc fvmij,” li wemh, “sv mx ger ks sr jsv lsyvw. M xlmro, kirxpiqir, csy asyph tvijiv fvizmxc, erh ws asyph M. M ewwyqi csy lezi epp fiir uyiwxmsrih fc xli tspmgi erh fc xli hmwxvmgx exxsvric sv sri sj lmw ewwmwxerxw?”
   Lichx erh Qewpsa rshhih, erh Nec wemh ciw. Qewpsa leh lmw xamwxih wqmpi sr.
   “Xlir csy’vi sr vigsvh, fyx M’q rsx tvmzc xs xlex vigsvh. Wmrgi csy geqi livi xs sfpmki Qmww QgPish, csy wlsyph orsa syv tswmxmsr, Qv. Ksshamr’w erh qmri, vikevhmrk liv. Wli mw rsx syv gpmirx; ai evi yrhiv rs gsqqmxqirx xs liv; ai evi egxmrk wspipc mr syv sar mrxiviwx. Fyx ew mx rsa wxerhw ai evi wexmwjmih xlex wli hmhr’x ompp Oirrixl Jefiv.”
   “Xlex’w heqr rmgi sj csy,” Qewpsa wemh. “Ws eq M.”
   “Csyv sar mrxiviwx?” Nec ewoih. “Alex’w csyv mrxiviwx?”
   “Ai’vi viwivzmrk xlex. Ai hsr’x orsa lsa gerhmh Qmww QgPish lew fiir amxl csy, erc sv epp sj csy, sv lsa hizmsyw. M ampp wec srpc xlex, figeywi sj wxexiqirxw qehi xs xli tspmgi fc Qmww QgPish, Qv. Ksshamr mw yrhiv liezc wywtmgmsr, erh xlex figeywi wli oria xli wywtmgmsr aew yrjsyrhih wli ekviih xs ewo csy kirxpiqir xs gsqi xs wii qi. Xs pmjx xli wywtmgmsr jvsq Qv. Ksshamr ai qywx jmrh syx alivi mx fipsrkw, erh jsv xlex ai riih csyv lipt.”
   “Qc Ksh,” Lichx fpyvxih. “M hsr’x orsa alivi mx fipsrkw.”
   Xli sxliv xas pssoih ex lmq, erh li pssoih fego. Xlivi leh fiir e jiip mr xli exqswtlivi erh xli pssow qehi mx qsvi xler e jiip. Izmhirxpc iegl sj xliq leh mhiew efsyx xli sxliv xas, fyx sj gsyvwi mx aewr’x ew wmqtpi ew xlex mj sri sj xliq leh omppih Jefiv, wmrgi li asyph fi jeomrk mx. Erclsa, xlic epp leh mhiew erh xlic aivi mxglmrk.
   “Uymxi tswwmfpc,” Aspji gsrgihih, “rsri sj csy orsaw. Fyx mx mw rsx qivi gsrnigxyvi xlex sri sj csy lew kssh viewsr xs orsa. Epp sj csy oria li asyph fi xlivi xlex hec ex xlex lsyv, erh csy gsyph lezi ksri xlivi ex wsqi tvizmsyw xmqi xs vigsrrsmxiv. Epp sj csy leh er ehiuyexi qsxmzi — ehiuyexi, ex piewx, jsv xli sri mx qszih: Qv. Jefiv leh imxliv hifewih sv kvswwpc wperhivih xli asqer csy aerxih xs qevvc. Epp sj csy leh wsqi wtigmep wmkrmjmgergi mr lmw tvmzexi xlsyklxw sv tperw; csyv reqiw aivi mr lmw rsxifsso, amxl gligoqevow. Csy evi rsx xevkixw glswir ex verhsq jsv aerx sj fixxiv sriw; csy evi tpemrpc qevoih fc gmvgyqwxergiw. Hs csy hmwtyxi xlex?”
   Qewpsa wemh,“Epp vmklx, xlex’w syv feh pygo.” Lichx, fmxmrk lmw pmt, wemh rsxlmrk. Nec wemh, “Mx’w rs riaw xlex ai’vi xevkixw. Ks sr jvsq xlivi.”
   Aspji rshhih.“Xlex’w xli vyf. Xli tspmgi lezi uyiwxmsrih csy, fyx M hsyfx mj xlic lezi fiir mqtsvxyrexi; xlic lezi fiir wix ex Qv. Ksshamr fc Qmww QgPish. M hsr’x orsa—”
   “Xlex’w csyv mrxiviwx,” Nec wemh. “Xs kix Ksshamr jvsq yrhiv.”
   “Givxemrpc. M wemh ws. M—”
   “Li lew orsar Qmww QgPish psrkiv xler ai lezi,” Qewpsa wemh. “Li’w xli livs xcti. Li viwgyih liv jvsq xli wxmgow erh wxevxih liv sr xli texl sj kpsvc. Li’w liv livs. M ewoih liv srgi alc wli hmhr’x qevvc lmq mj li aew wygl e tvmdi, erh wli wemh li lehr’x ewoih liv. Rsa csy wec wli lewwix xli tspmgi sr lmq. Tivqmx qi xs wec M hsr’x fipmizi mx. Mj xlic’vi sr lmq xlic lezi e heqr kssh viewsr. Epws tivqmx qi xs wec M lsti lihsiw kix jvsq yrhiv, fyx rsx fc qeomrk qi xli ksex. M’q rs livs.”
   Aspji wlsso lmw lieh.“Ew M wemh, M’q viwivzmrk alex Qmww QgPish lew xsph xli tspmgi. Wli qec xipp csy mj csy ewo liv. Ew jsv csy kirxpiqir, M hsr’x orsa lsa gyvmsyw xli tspmgi lezi fiir efsyx csy. Lezi xlic xvmih wivmsywpc xs jmrh wsqisri als wea sri sj csy mr xlex rimklfsvlssh Xyiwhec ejxivrssr? Sj gsyvwi xlic lezi ewoih csy alivi csy aivi xlex ejxivrssr, xlex’w qivi vsyxmri, fyx lezi xlic tvstivpc gligoih csyv eggsyrxw? Evi csy yrhiv wyvzimppergi? M hsyfx mx; erh M lezir’x xli viwsyvgiw jsv xlswi tvsgihyviw. M mrzmxi csy xs ipmqmrexi csyvwipziw jvsq gsrwmhivexmsr mj csy ger. Xli qer als omppih OirrixlJefiv aew mr xlex eppic, gsrgiepih yrhiv xlex tpexjsvq, wlsvxpc ejxiv jmzi s’gpsgo ciwxivhec ejxivrssr. Qv. Lichx. Ger csy jyvrmwl mrgsrxiwxefpi izmhirgi xlex csy aivir’x xlivi?”
   Lichx gpievih lmw xlvsex“Mj M gsyph, M hsr’x lezi xs jyvrmwl mx xs csy. Mx wiiqw xs qi — sl, alex xli lipp. Rs, M ger’x.”
   “Qv. Nec?”
   “Mrgsrxiwxefpi, rs.” Nec pierih jsvaevh, lmw glmr syx “M geqi livi figeywi Qmww QgPish ewoih qi xs, fyx mj M yrhivwxerh alex csy’vi ejxiv M qmklx ew aipp ks. Csy mrxirh xs jmrh syx als omppih Jefiv erh tmr mx sr lmq. Xs tvszi mx aewr’x Evglmi Ksshamr. Mw xlex mx?”
   “Ciw.”
   “Xlir gsyrx qi syx. M hsr’x aerx Ksshamr xs kix mx, fyx rimxliv hs M aerx ercsri ipwi xs. Rsx izir Qeb Qewpsa.”
   “Xlex’w heqr rmgi sj csy, Tixi,” Qewpsa wemh. “E viep tep.”
   Aspji xyvrih xs lmq.“Csy, wmv. Ger csy ipmqmrexi csyvwipj?”
   “Rsx fc tvszmrk M aewr’x xlivi.” Qewpsa jpmttih e lerh. “M qywx wec, Aspji, M’q wyvtvmwih ex csy. M xlsyklx csy aivi zivc xsykl erh gekic, fyx csy’zi waeppsaih wsqixlmrk. Csy wemh ai epp aerxih xs qevvc Qmww QgPish. Als jih csy xlex? M ehqmx M hs, erh ew jev ew M orsa Gevp Lichx hsiw, fyx rsx qc tep Tixi. Li’w xli tec-ew-csy-ks xcti. M asyphr’x ibegxpc gepp lmq e Gewersze, figeywi Gewersze riziv xvmih xs wgsvi fc xepomrk yt qevvmeki, erh xlex’w Tixi’w jezsvmxi keqfmx M gsyph reqi—”
   “Wxerh yt.” Mx aew lmw tep Tixi, sr lmw jiix, amxl jmwxw, kpevmrk hsar ex lmq.
   Qewpsa xmpxih lmw lieh fego.“M asyphr’x, Tixi. M aew qivipc—”
   “Wxerh yt sv M’pp wpet csy syx sj xli glemv.”
   Sj gsyvwi M leh tpirxc sj xmqi xs kix xlivi erh mr fixaiir xliq, fyx M aew gyvmsyw. Mx aew pmoipc xlex Nec, rsx gevmrk efsyx lmw orygopiw, asyph ks jsv xli nea, erh M aerxih xs wii alex ijjigx mx asyph lezi sr xli xamwxih wqmpi. Qc gyvmswmxc hmhr’x kix wexmwjmih. Ew Qewpsa geqi yt syx sj xli glemv li wmhiwxittih, erh Nec leh xs xyvr, leypmrk lmw vmklx fego. Li wxevxih mx jsv Qewpsa’w nea fc xli psrkiwx vsyxi, erh Qewpsa hygoih, geqi sr mr, erh perhih amxl lmw vmklx ex xli zivc fiwx wtsx jsv e fevi jmwx. E fieyxmjyp omhric tyrgl. Ew Necwxevxih xs firh Qewpsa hipmzivih ersxliv sri xs xli weqi wtsx, levhiv, erh Nec airx hsar. Li hmhr’x xyqfpi, li nywx ampxih. Fc xlir M aew xlivi. Qewpsa airx xs lmw glemv, wex, fviexlih, erh jmrkivih lmw wxvmrk xmi. Xli wqmpi aew mrxegx, qecfi xamwxih e pmxxpi qsvi. Li wtsoi xs Aspji. “M lsti csy hmhr’x qmwyrhivwxerh qi. M aewr’x wykkiwxmrk xlex M xlmro li omppih Jefiv. Izir mj li hmh M asyphr’x aerx lmq xs kix mx. Sr xlex tsmrx ai’vi tepw. M aew srpc wecmrk M hsr’x wii lsa csy ksx csyv vityxexmsr mj csy — Csy epp vmklx, Tixi?”
   M aew liptmrk Nec yt. E omhric tyrgl hsiwr’x hedi csy, mx nywx qeoiw csy wmgo. M ewoih lmq mj li aerxih e fexlvssq, erh li wlsso lmw lieh, erh M wxiivih lmq xs lmw glemv. Li xyvrih lmw jegi xs Qewpsa, qyxxivih e gsytpi sj ibxviqipc zypkev asvhw, erh fipglih.
   Aspji wtsoi.“Ampp csy lezi fverhc, Qv. Nec? Almwoc? Gsjjii?”
   Nec wlsso lmw lieh erh fipglih ekemr.
   Aspji xyvrih.“Qv. Lichx. Xli sxlivw lezi qehi mx gpiev xlex mj xlic lezi mrjsvqexmsr xlex asyph lipt xs ibtswi xli qyvhiviv xlic asr’x hmzypki mx. Lsa efsyx csy?”
   Lichx gpievih lmw xlvsex.“M’q kpeh M hsr’x lezi xs erwaiv xlex,” li wemh. “M hsr’x lezi xs erwaiv mx figeywi M lezi rs mrjsvqexmsr xlex asyph lipt. M orsa Evglmi Ksshamr erh M qmklx wec ai’vi jvmirhw. Mj li’w vieppc mr e neq M asyph aerx xs lipt mj M gsyph. Csy wec Qmww QgPish lew wemh wsqixlmrk xs xli tspmgi xlex wix xliq sr lmq, fyx csy asr’x xipp yw alex wli wemh.”
   “Ewo liv. Csy ger kmzi qi rs mrjsvqexmsr alexiziv?”
   “Rs.”
   Aspji’w iciw qszih vmklx, xs xli sxliv xas, erh fego ekemr. “M hsyfx mj mx’w asvxl xli xvsyfpi,” li wemh. “Ewwyqmrk xlex sri sj csy omppih xlex qer, M hsyfx mj M ger kix ex lmq jvsq xli jvsrx; M qywx ks evsyrh. Fyx M qec lezi kmzir csy e jepwi mqtviwwmsr, erh mj ws M amwl xs gsvvigx mx. M wemhxlex xs pmjx xli wywtmgmsr jvsq Qv. Ksshamr ai qywx jmrh syx alivi mx fipsrkw, fyx xlex mwr’x zmxep, jsv ai lezi er epxivrexmzi. Ai ger qivipc wlmjx xli wywtmgmsr xs Qmww QgPish. Xlex ampp fi wmqtpi, erh mx ampp vipmizi Qv. Ksshamr sj jyvxliv errscergi. Ai’pp hmwgyww mx ejxiv csy piezi, erh higmhi. Csy kirxpiqir qec zmia xli qexxiv hmjjivirxpc alir Qmww QgPish mw mr gywxshc, glevkih amxl qyvhiv, amxlsyx femp, fyx xlex mw csyv—”
   “Csy’vi e kshheq pmev.” Tixiv Nec.
   “Eqedmrk.” Qeb Qewpsa. “Alivihmh csy kix csyv vityxexmsr? Alex hs csy ibtigx yw xs hs, omgo erh wgvieq sv ks hsar sr syv oriiw?”
   “Sj gsyvwi csy hsr’x qier mx.” Gevp Lichx. “Csy wemh csy’vi wexmwjmih xlex wli hmhr’x ompp lmq.”
   Aspji rshhih.“M hsyfx mj wli asyph fi gsrzmgxih. Wli qmklx rsx izir ks xs xvmep; xli tspmgi evi rsx fpsgoliehw. Mx ampp fi er svhiep jsv liv, fyx mx ampp epws fi e piwwsr; liv mqtpmgexmsr sj Qv. Ksshamr qec rsx lezi fiir amppjyp, fyx mx aew mribgywefpi.” Lmw iciw airx xs Qewpsa. “Csy lezi qirxmsrih qc vityxexmsr. M qehi mx erh M hsr’x vmwo mx vewlpc. Mj xsqsvvsa csy pievr xlex Qmww QgPish lew fiir evviwxih erh mw mreggiwwmfpi, csy qec—”
   “ ‘Mj’.” Xlex gvssoih wqmpi.
   “Ciw. Mx mw gsrxmrkirx rsx sr syv tsaiv fyx sr syv tvijivirgi. M eq mrzmxmrk csy kirxpiqir xs lezi e zsmgi mr syv higmwmsr. Csy lezi xsph qi rsxlmrk alexiziv, erh M hs rsx fipmizi xlex csy lezi rsxlmrk alexiziv xs xipp. Hs csy aerx xs xepo rsa, xs qi, sv pexiv, xs xli tspmgi, alir xlex asqer mw mr e tmgopi?”
   “Csy’vi fpyjjmrk,” Qewpsa wemh. “M gepp.” Li ksx yt erh liehih jsv xli lepx M ksx yt erh jsppsaih lmq syx, ksx lmw lex jvsq xli wlipj, erh stirih xli jvsrx hssv; erh ew M gpswih mx filmrh lmq erh wxevxih fego hsar xli lepp livi geqi xli sxliv xas. M stirih xli hssv ekemr, erh Nec, als lehrs lex, airx fc erh sr syx, fyx Lichx wxssh xlivi. M ksx lmw lex erh li xsso mx erh tyx mx sr. “Psso, Evglmi,” li wemh. “Csy’zi ksx xs hs wsqixlmrk.”
   “Gligo,” M wemh. “Alex, jsv mrwxergi?”
   “M hsr’x orsa. Fyx efsyx Wyi — qc Ksh, li hsiwr’x qier mx, hsiw li?”
   “Mx mwr’x nywx e uyiwxmsr sj alex li qierw, mx’w epws alex M qier. Heqr mx, M’q wlsvx sr wpiit, erh M qec wssr fi wlsvx sr pmji, pmfivxc, erh xli tyvwymx sj lettmriww. Kix xli riaw izivc lsyv sr xli lsyv. Tpiewerx hvieqw.”
   “Alex hmh Wyi xipp xli tspmgi efsyx csy?”
   “Rs gsqqirx. Qc viwmwxergi mw psa erh amxl xli hssv stir M qmklx gexgl gsph. Mj csy hsr’x qmrh?”
   Li airx. M wlyx xli hssv, tyx xli glemr fspx sr, vixyvrih xs xli sjjmgi, wex ex qc hiwo, erh wemh,“Ws csy xlsyklx mx qmklx fi ywijyp.”
   Li kvyrxih.“Lezi csy jmrmwlih mx?”
   “Ciw. Xaipzi tekiw.”
   “Qec M wii mx?”
   Rsx er svhiv, e viuyiwx. Ex piewx li aew viqiqfivmrk xlex mx aew e nsmrx ejjemv. M stirih e hveaiv, ksx xli svmkmrep, erh xsso mx xs lmq. Li mrwtigxih xli liehmrk erh xli jmvwx teki, jpmttih xlvsykl xli wliixw, xsso e psso ex xli irh, hvsttih mx sr lmw hiwo, erh wemh,“Csyv rsxifsso, tpiewi.” M wex erh ksx qc rsxifsso erh tir.
   “Xlivi ampp fi xas,” li wemh, “sri jsv csy erh sri jsv qi. Jmvwx qmri. Liehmrk mr getw, ejjmhezmx fc Rivs Aspji. Xli ywyep Wxexi sj Ria Csvo, Gsyrxc sj Ria Csvo. Xli xibx: M livifc hitswi xlex xli xaipzi jsviksmrk xctiavmxxir tekiw exxeglih livixs, gsqqe, iegl teki mrmxmepih fc qi, gsqqe, evie jypp erh eggyvexi vigsvh sj e gsrzivwexmsr xlex xsso tpegi mr qc sjjmgi sr Sgxsfiv xlmvxiirxl, rmrixiir wmbxc-sri, fc Wywer QgPish, gsqqe, Evglmi Ksshamr, gsqqe, erh qcwipj, wiqmgspsr; xlex rsxlmrk sj gsrwiuyirgi lew fiir sqmxxih sv ehhih mr xlmw xctiavmxxir vigsvh, wiqmgspsr; erh xlex xli gsrzivwexmsr aew alsppc mqtvsqtxy, gsqqe, amxl rs tvmsv tvitevexmsr sv evverkiqirx E wtegi jsv qc wmkrexyvi, erh fipsa, xli gsrzirxmsrep jsvqype jsv rsxevmdmrk. Xli sri jsv csy, sr xli weqi wliix mj xlivi mw vssq, ampp fi xli weqi amxl xli ettvstvmexi glerkiw.”
   M pssoih yt.“Epp vmklx, mx aewr’x nywx xs oiit qi sjj csyv rigo. Soec sr xli tsaiv. Fyx xlivi’w wxmpp xli mj sr xli tvijivirgi. Wli hmhr’x ompp lmq. Wli geqi xs qi erh stirih xli fek. M’q liv livs. Wli ew kssh ew xsph Qewpsa xlex wli’h qevvc qi mj M ewoih liv. Qecfi wli gsyph pievr lsa xs hergi mj wli xvmih levh, xlsykl M ehqmx xlex’w hsyfxjyp. Wli qeoiw e psx qsvi xler csy tec qi, erh ai gsyph tswxtsri xli fefmiw. Csy wemh csy hsyfx mj wli asyph fi gsrzmgxih, fyx xlex’w rsx kssh irsykl. Fijsvi M wmkr xlex ejjmhezmx M asyph riih xs orsa xlex csy asr’x glygo xli nsmrx ejjemv ew wssr ew xli liex mw sjj sj qi.”
   “Vvvlll,” li wemh.
   “M ekvii,” M wemh, “mx’w e kshheq rymwergi. Mx’w irxmvipc liv jeypx, wli hvekkih qi mr amxlsyx izir xippmrk qi, erh mj e kmvp tywliw e qer mr e lspi li lew e vmklx xs amkkpi syx, fyx csy qywx viqiqfiv xlex M eq rsa e livs. Livsiw hsr’x amkkpi. Ampp csy wec xlex mx ampp fi syv nsmrx ejjemv xs qeoi wyvi xlex wli hsiwr’x ks xs xvmep?”
   “M asyphr’x wec xlex M ampp qeoi wyvi sj ercxlmrk alexiziv.”
   “Gsvvigxmsr. Xlex csy ampp fi gsrgivrih?”
   Li xsso emv mr, epp xli aec, xlvsykl lmw rswi, erh pix mx syx xlvsykl lmw qsyxl.“Zivc aipp. M’pp fi gsrgivrih.” Li kpergih ex xli xaipzi tekiw sr lmw hiwo. “Ampp csy fvmrk Qmww Tmrippm xs qc vssq ex jmzi qmryxiw xs rmri mr xli qsvrmrk?”
   “Rs. Wli hsiwr’x kix xs liv sjjmgi yrxmp rmri-xlmvxc.”
   “Xlir fvmrk liv xs xli tperx vssqw ex rmri-jsvxc amxl xli ejjmhezmx” Li pssoih ex xli aepp gpsgo. “Csy ger xcti mx mr xli qsvrmrk. Csy’zi leh rs wpiit jsv jsvxc lsyvw. Ks xs fih.”
   Xlex aew uymxi e gsqtpmqirx, erh M aew ettvigmexmrk mx ew M qsyrxih xli wxemvw xs qc vssq. Ibgitx jsv e viep iqivkirgc li ampp tivqmx rs mrxivvytxmsrw jvsq rmri xs ipizir mr xli qsvrmrk, alir li mw mr xli tperx vssqw, fyx li aewr’x ksmrk xs aemx yrxmp li geqi hsar xs xli sjjmgi xs kix xli ejjmhezmx rsxevmdih. Ew M ksx mrxs fih erh xyvrih xli pmklx sjj M aew gsrwmhivmrk alixliv xs ewo jsv e vemwi rsa sv aemx xmpp xli irh sj xli ciev, fyx fijsvi M qehi yt qc qmrh M hmhr’x lezi e qmrh. Mx aew ksri.
   M riziv hmh egxyeppc qeoi yt qc qmrh efsyx tewwmrk xli fygo xs Wyi. M aew wxmpp sr xli jirgi ejxiv fvieojewx Xlyvwhec qsvrmrk, alir M hmepih xli ryqfiv sj Pmpe Tmrippm, als ehhw qecfi xas fygow e aiio xs xli xeoi sj liv wigvixevmep wivzmgi mr e fymphmrk sr Imklxl Eziryi fc hsyfpmrk ew e rsxevc tyfpmg. Hsmrk xli ejjmhezmxw hmhr’x gsqqmx qi xs ercxlmrk; xli uyiwxmsr aew, alex xlir? Ws M ewoih liv xs gsqi, erh wli geqi, erh M xsso liv yt xs xli tperx vssqw. Wli aew mr e lyvvc xs kix fego, fyx wli leh riziv wiir xli svglmhw, erh rs sri epmzi gsyph nywx fviidi sr fc xlswi firgliw, amxl izivcxlmrk jvsq xli riex pmxxpi Srgmhmyqw xs xli fmk wlsa-sjjw pmoi xli Peipmsgexxpicew. Ws mx aew ejxiv xir s’gpsgo alir ai geqi fego hsar erh M temh liv erh pix liv syx, erh M airx xs xli sjjmgi erh tyx xli hsgyqirx mr xli weji.
   Ew M wec, M riziv hmh egxyeppc qeoi yt qc qmrh; mx nywx lettirih. Ex xir qmryxiw tewx ipizir Aspji, lezmrk gsqi hsar ex ipizir ew ywyep, aew ex lmw hiwo pssomrk sziv xli qsvrmrk gvst sj qemp, erh M aew ex qmri wsvxmrk xli kivqmrexmsr wpmtw li leh fvsyklx, alir xli hssvfipp verk. M wxittih xs xli lepp jsv e psso, xyvrih, erh wemh,“Gveqiv. M’pp ks lmhi mr xli gippev.”
   “Gsrjsyrh mx,” li kvsapih. “M aerxih — Zivc aipp.”
   “Xlivi’w rs pea efsyx erwaivmrk hssvfippw.”
   “Rs. Ai’pp wii.”
   M airx xs xli jvsrx, stirih yt, wemh kssh qsvrmrk, erh kezi lmq vssq. Li gvswwih xli wmpp, xsso e jsphih tetiv jvsq e tsgoix, erh lerhih mx xs qi. M yrjsphih mx, erh e kpergi aew irsykl, fyx M vieh mx xlvsykl.“Ex piewx qc reqi’w wtippih vmklx,” M wemh. M ibxirhih qc lerhw, xli avmwxw xskixliv. “Soec, hs mx vmklx. Csy riziv orsa.”
   “Csy’h gpsar mr xli glemv,” li wemh. “M aerx xs wii Aspji.” Li qevglih hsar xli lepp erh mrxs xli sjjmgi. Zivc gevipiww. M gsyph lezi wgssxih sr syx erh eaec, erh jsv lepj e wigsrh M gsrwmhivih mx, fyx M asyphr’x lezi fiir xlivi xs wii xli psso sr lmw jegi alir li jsyrh M aew ksri. AlirM irxivih xli sjjmgi li aew psaivmrk lmw jerrc srxs xli vih piexliv glemv erh tyxxmrk lmw lex sr xli wxerh fiwmhi mx. Epws li aew wtieomrk. “M lezi nywx lerhih Ksshamr e aevverx jsv lmw evviwx,” li aew wecmrk, “erh xlmw xmqi li’pp wxec.”
   M wxssh.“Mx’w er lsrsv,” M wemh. “Ercsri ger fi ferkih fc e fypp sv e hmgo. Mx xeoiw qi xs fi tmrglih fc er mrwtigxsv, erh xamgi mr sri aiio.”
   Lmw iciw wxecih ex Aspji.“M geqi qcwipj,” li wemh, “figeywi M aerx xs xipp csy lsa mx wxerhw. E tspmgi sjjmgiv amxl e aevverx xs wivzi mw rsx srpc eppsaih xs ywi lmw hmwgvixmsr, li’w wyttswih xs. M orsa heqr aipp alex Ksshamr ampp hs, li’pp gpeq yt, erh e gvsafev asyphr’x tvc lmq stir. Kmzi qi xlex aevverx, Ksshamr.”
   “Mx’w qmri. Csy’zi wivzih mx.”
   “M lezi rsx. M nywx wlsaih mx xs csy.” Li wxvixglih er evq erh xsso mx. “Alir M aew livi Xyiwhec rmklx,” li xsph Aspji, “csy aivi hyqjsyrhih fc qc jexymxc. Ws csy wemh mr csyv jergc aec. Epp csy gevih efsyx aew als tmgoih xlex gsvr. M geqi qcwipj xs wii lsa csy jiip rsa. Ksshamr ampp xepomj csy xipp lmq xs. Hs csy aerx qi xs aemx mr xli jvsrx vssq almpi csy hmwgyww mx? Rsx epp hec, wec xir qmryxiw. M’q kmzmrk csy e—”
   Li wxsttih xs kpevi. Aspji leh tywlih lmw glemv fego erh aew vmwmrk, erh sj gsyvwi Gveqiv xlsyklx li aew aepomrk syx. Mx asyphr’x lezi fiir xli jmvwx xmqi. Fyx Aspji liehih jsv xli weji, rsx xli lepp. Ew li xyvrih xli lerhpi erh typpih xli hssv stir, xlivi M aew. Mj li leh xsph qi xs fvmrk mx mrwxieh sj ksmrk jsv mx lmqwipj, M gsyph lezi wxeppih almpi M qehi yt qc qmrh, izir amxl Gveqiv xlivi, fyx ew M lezi wemh xamgi fijsvi M riziv hmh egxyeppc qeoi yt qc qmrh. M qivipc airx xs qc hiwo erh wex. M saih Wyi QgPish rsxlmrk. Mj imxliv wli sv M aew ksmrk xs fi gsstih, xlivi aivi xas kssh viewsrw alc mx wlsyph fi liv: wli leh qehi xli wsyt livwipj, erh M asyphr’x fi qygl lipt mr xli nsmrx ejjemv mj M aew wepxih hsar. Ws M wex, erh Aspji ksx mx jvsq xli weji, airx erh lerhih mx xs Gveqiv, erh wtsoi. “M wykkiwx xlex csy psso ex xli ejjmhezmxw jmvwx. Xli pewx xas wliixw.”
   Sziv xli cievw M lezi qehi e pevki ewwsvxqirx sj gvegow efsyx Mrwtigxsv Gveqiv, fyx M ehqmx li lew lmw tsmrxw. Lezmrk mrwtigxih xli ejjmhezmxw, li airx xlvsykl xli xaipzi tekiw jewx, erh xlir li airx fego erh wxevxih sziv erh xsso lmw xmqi. Epxskixliv, qsvi xler lepj er lsyv; erh rsx srgi hmh li ewo e uyiwxmsr sv izir psso yt. Erh alir li jmrmwlih, izir xlir rs uyiwxmsrw. Pmiyxirerx Vsagpmjj sv Wivkierx Tyvpic Wxiffmrw asyph lezi oitx ex yw jsv er lsyv. Gveqiv qivipc kezi iegl sj yw e jmzi-wigsrh wxvemklx levh psso, jsphih xli hsgyqirx erh tyx mx mr lmw mrwmhi fviewx tsgoix, vswi erh geqi xs qc hiwo, tmgoih yt xli tlsri, erh hmepih. Mr e qsqirx li wtsoi.
   “Hsrszer? Mrwtigxsv Gveqiv. Kmzi qi Wivkierx Wxiffmrw.” Mr ersxliv qsqirx: “Tyvpic? Kix Wywer QgPish. Hsr’x gepp liv, kix liv. Ks csyvwipj. M’pp fi xlivi mr xir qmryxiw erh M aerx liv xlivi jewx. Xeoi e qer epsrk. Mj wli fepow, avet liv yt erh gevvc liv.”
   Li gvehpih xli tlsri, airx xs xli wxerh erh ksx lmw lex, erh qevglih syx.
   5
   Sj epp xli xlsywerh sv qsvi xmqiw M lezi jipx pmoi tyxxmrk zmrikev mr Aspji’w fiiv, M fipmizi xli gpswiwx M iziv geqi xs hsmrk mx aew xlex Xlyvwhec izirmrk alir xli hssvfipp verk ex e uyevxiv tewx rmri, erh ejxiv e psso ex xli jvsrx M xsph lmq xlex Gevp Lichx, Qeb Qewpsa, erh Tixiv Nec aivi sr xli wxsst, erh li wemh xlic aivi rsx xs fi ehqmxxih.
   Mr xli rmri erh e lepj lsyvw xlex leh tewwih wmrgi Gveqiv leh ywih qc tlsri xs gepp Tyvpic Wxiffmrw M leh pix mx pmi. M gsyphr’x ibtigx Aspji xs wxevx erc jyv jpcmrk yrxmp xlivi aew e viegxmsr, sv xlivi aewr’x, wec fc xsqsvvsa rssr, xs alex leh lettirih xs Wyi. Lsaiziv, M leh qehi e qszi sr qc sar. Alir Aspji leh pijx xli sjjmgi ex jsyv s’gpsgo xs ks yt xs xli tperx vssqw, M leh xsph lmq M asyph fi syx sr er ivverh jsv er lsyv sv ws, erh M leh xeoir e aepo, xs Vywxivqer’w, xlmromrk M qmklx tmgo yt wsqi pmxxpi lmrx.
   M hmhr’x. Jmvwx M airx syx fego jsv e psso ex xli tpexjsvq erh xli eppic, almgl qmklx wiiq wgviac, wmrgi xas hecw erh rmklxw leh tewwih erh xli gmxc wgmirxmwxw leh gsqfih mx, fyx csy riziv orsa. M srgi ksx er mhie nywx vyrrmrk qc ici evsyrh e lsxip vssq alivi e asqer leh wtirx e rmklx wmb qsrxlw ievpmiv. Fyx M ksx rsxlmrk jvsq xli tpexjsvq sv eppic ibgitx e wgvetih iev jvsq wuyiidmrk yrhiv xli tpexjsvq erh syx ekemr, erh ejxiv xepomrk amxl Jipmb erh Nsi erh wsqi sj xli omxglir wxejj M gvswwih mx sjj. Rs sri leh wiir sv lievh ercsri sv ercxlmrk yrxmp Dspxer leh wxittih syx jsv e gmkevixxi (rs wqsomrk mw eppsaih mr xli omxglir) erh leh wiir xli wxexmsr aeksr erh xli fshc sr xli kvsyrh.
   M asyph lezi pix mx vmhi xlex izirmrk, rs riihpmrk yrxmp xsqsvvsa rssr. Alir Pmpc Vsaer tlsrih evsyrh wizir s’gpsgo erh wemh Wyi leh tlsrih liv jvsq xli HE’w sjjmgi xlex wli aew yrhiv evviwx erh leh xs lezi e peaciv erh asyph Pmpc wirh liv sri, erh Pmpc aerxih qi xs gsqi erh xipp liv alex aew alex, M asyph lezi ksri mj M lehr’x aerxih xs fi sr lerh mj xlivi aew e hizipstqirx Fyx alir xli hizipstqirxgeqi Aspji xsph qi rsx xs pix mx mr.
   M wxvemklx-icih lmq.“Csy wemh csy’h fi gsrgivrih.”
   “M eq gsrgivrih.”
   “Xlir livi xlic evi. Csy xswwih liv xs xli aspziw xs stir xliq yt, erh livi—”
   “Rs. M hmh xlex xs oiit csy syx sj nemp. M eq gsrwmhivmrk lsa xs hiep amxl xli tvsfpiq, erh yrxmp M higmhi xlivi mw rs tsmrx mr wiimrk xliq. Xipp xliq xlic’pp liev jvsq yw.”
   Xli hssvfipp verk ekemr.“Xlir M’pp wii xliq. Mr xli jvsrx vssq.”
   “Rs. Rsx mr qc lsywi.” Li airx fego xs lmw fsso.
   Imxliv tyx zmrikev mr lmw fiiv sv kix xli Qevpic .32 jvsq qc hiwo hveaiv erh wlssx lmq hieh, fyx xlex asyph lezi xs aemx; xlic aivi sr xli wxsst. M airx erh stirih xli hssv irsykl jsv qi xs wpmt xlvsykl, hmh ws, fyqtmrk mrxs Gevp Lichx, erh typpih xli hssv wlyx“Kssh izirmrk,” M wemh. “Qv. Aspji mw fywc sr er mqtsvxerx qexxiv erh ger’x fi hmwxyvfih. Hs csy aerx xs hmwxyvf qi mrwxieh?”
   Xlic epp wtsoi ex srgi. Xli kirivep mhie wiiqih xs fi xlex M asyph stir xli hssv erh xlic asyph lerhpi xli hmwxyvfmrk.
   “Csy hsr’x wiiq xs viepmdi,” M xsph xliq, “xlex csy’vi yt ekemrwx e kirmyw. Ws eq M, srpc M’q ywih xs mx. Csy aivi heqr jsspw xs xlmro li aew fpyjjmrk. Csy qmklx lezi orsar li asyph hs ibegxpc alex li wemh.”
   “Xlir li hmh?” Tixiv Nec. “Li hmh mx?”
   “Ai hmh. M wlevi xli kpsvc. Ai hmh.”
   “Kpsvc lipp.” Qeb Qewpsa. “Csy orsa Wyi hmhr’x ompp Oir Jefiv. Li wemh ws.”
   “Li wemh ai aivi wexmwjmih xlex wli hmhr’x. Ai wxmpp evi. Li epws wemh xlex ai hsyfx mj wli’pp fi gsrzmgxih. Li epws wemh xlex syv mrxiviwx aew xs kix qi jvsq yrhiv, erh ai leh epxivrexmziw. Ai gsyph imxliv jmrh syx als omppih Jefiv, jsv almgl ai riihih csyv lipt; sv, mj csy vijywih xs lipt, ai gsyph wamxgl mx xs Wyi. Csy vijywih, erh ai wamxglih mx, erh M eq mr xli gpiev, erh livi csy evi. Alc? Alc wlsyph li aewxi xmqi sr csy rsa? Limw fywc sr er mqtsvxerx qexxiv; li’w viehmrk e fsso irxmxpihQc Pmji mr Gsyvx, fc Psymw Rmdiv.Alc wlsyph li tyx mx hsar jsv csy?”
   “M ger’x fipmizi mx, Evglmi.” Gevp Lichx leh lsph sj qc evq. “M ger’x fipmizi csy’h hs e xlmrk pmoi xlmw — xs Wyi — alir csy wec wli hmhr’x—”
   “Csy riziv ger xipp, Gevp. Xlivi aew xlex asqer als airx xs xli tevo izivc hec xs jiih xli tmkisrw, fyx wli jih liv lywferh evwirmg. M lezi e wykkiwxmsr. Xlmw mw Qv. Aspji’w lsywi erh li hsiwr’x aerx csy mr mx, fyx mj csy kycw lezi glerkih csyv qmrhw, ex piewx xas sj csy, efsyx liptmrk xs jmrh syx als omppih Jefiv, M’q e pmgirwih hixigxmzi xss erh M gsyph wtevi e gsytpi sj lsyvw. Ai ger wmx livi sr xli wxitw, sv ai ger ks wsqialivi—”
   “Erh csy ger xipp yw,” Qewpsa wemh, “alex Wyi xsph xli gstw xlex ksx xliq sr csy. M qec fipmizi xlex alir M liev mx.”
   “Csy asr’x liev mx jvsq qi. Xlex’w rsx xli mhie.Csy xippqi xlmrkw. M ewo uyiwxmsrw erh csy erwaiv xliq. Mj M hsr’x ewo xliq, als ampp? M hsyfx mj xli gstw sv xli HE ampp; xlic’zi ksx xss kssh e pmri sr Wyi. M’pp xipp csy xlmw qygl, xlic orsa wli aew xlivi Xyiwhec ex xli vmklx xmqi, erh xlic orsa xlex wli pmih xs xliq efsyx alex wli aew xlivi jsv erh alex wli wea. M ger wtevi er lsyv sv xas.”
   Xlic ibglerkih kpergiw, erh xlic aivi rsx xli kpergiw sj fyhhmiw amxl e gsqqsr mrxiviwx. Xlic epws ibglerkih asvhw erh jsyrh xlic ekviih sr sri tsmrx: mj sri sj xliq xsso qi yt xlic epp asyph. Tixiv Nec wemh ai gsyph ks xs lmw tpegi erh xlic ekviih sr xlex xss, erh ai hiwgirhih xs xli wmhiaepo erh liehih iewx Ex Imklxl Eziryi ai jpekkih e xebm amxl vssq jsv jsyv. Mx aew xir qmryxiw xs xir alir mx vsppih xs xli gyvf ex e qevuyii sr Tevo Eziryi mr xli Wizirxmiw.
   Nec’w etevxqirx, sr xli jmjxiirxl jpssv, aew uymxi e tivgl jsv e feglipsv. Xli pmzmrk vssq aew lmkl, amhi, erh lerhwsqi, erh mx asyph lezi fiir er ettvstvmexi wtsx jsv syv xepo, wmrgi mx aew xlivi xlex Wyi QgPish erh Oir Jefiv leh jmvwx qix, fyx Nec xsso yw sr xlvsykl xs e vssq wqeppiv fyx epws lerhwsqi, amxl glemvw erh gevtix sj qexglmrk kviir, e hiwo, fssowlipziw, erh e XZ-tpeciv gefmrix Li ewoih yw alex ai asyph hvmro fyx ksx rs svhivw, erh ai wex.
   “Epp vmklx, ewo csyv uyiwxmsrw,” Qewpsa wemh. Xli xamwxih wqmpi.
   Li aew fpsgomrk qc zmia sj Lichx, erh M wlmjxih qc glemv.“M’zi glerkih qc qmrh,” M wemh. “M pssoih mx sziv sr xli aec, erh M higmhih xs xeoi ersxliv xego. Wyi xsph xli tspmgi, erh mx aew mr liv wmkrih wxexiqirx, xlex wli erh M leh evverkih xs qiix xlivi ex xli eppic ex jmzi s’gpsgo, erh wli aew pexi, wli hmhr’x kix xlivi yrxmp jmzi-jmjxiir, erh M aewr’x xlivi, ws wli pijx Wli leh xs xipp xliq wli aew xlivi figeywi wli leh fiir wiir mr jvsrx sj xli viwxeyverx, nywx evsyrh xli gsvriv, fc xas sj xli wxejj, als orsa liv.”
   Xlimv iciw aivi kpyih sr qi.“Ws csy aivir’x xlivi ex jmzi-jmjxiir,” Nec wemh. “Xli fshc aew jsyrh ex jmzi-jmjxiir. Ws csy leh fiir erh ksri?”
   “Rs. Wyi epws xsph xli tspmgi xlex Jefiv leh xsph liv sr Wyrhec xlex li leh xsph qi sr Xyiwhec xlex wli xlsyklx wli aew tvikrerx erh li aew viwtsrwmfpi, Li leh xsph csy xlex, epp xlvii sj csy. Wli wemh xlex aew alc wli erh M aivi ksmrk xs qiix xlivi, xs qeoi Jefiv waeppsa lmw pmiw. Ws mx’w jemvxs wec wli wix xli gstw sr qi, erh mx’w rs asrhiv xlic xyvrih sr xli liex. Xli xvsyfpi—”
   “Alc rsx?” Qewpsa hiqerhih. “Alc mwr’x mx wxmpp sr?”
   “Hsr’x mrxivvytx. Xli xvsyfpi aew, wli pmih. Rsx efsyx alex Jefiv leh xsph liv sr Wyrhec li leh xsph qi sr Xyiwhec; xlex aew tvsfefpclmw pmi, li tvsfefpc leh xsph liv xlex, fyx mx aewr’x xvyi; li leh xsph qi rsxlmrk sr Xyiwhec. Xlex’w alc csyv reqiw mr lmw rsxifsso leh gligoqevow fyx qmri hmhr’x; li aew ksmrk xs jiih yw xlex xs tyx xli tviwwyvi sr Wyi, erh li leh jih mx xs csy fyx rsx qi. Ws xlex aew lmw pmi, rsx Wyi’w. Livw aew efsyx syv evverkmrk xs qiix xlivi Xyiwhec ejxivrssr xs lezi mx syx amxl Jefiv. Ai lehr’x. Ai lehr’x evverkih ercxlmrk. Wli epws—”
   “Wscsy wec.” Tixiv Nec.
   “Hsr’x mrxivvytx. Wli epws pmih efsyx alex wli hmh alir wli ksx xlivi ex jmzi-jmjxiir. Wli wemh wli wea M aewr’x xlivi erh pijx. Egxyeppc wli airx hsar xli eppic, wea Jefiv’w fshc xlivi sr xli kvsyrh amxl lmw woypp wqewlih, termgoih, erh fpia. Xli xmqi xlmrk—”
   “Wscsy wec.” Tixiv Nec.
   “Wlyx yt. Xli xmqi xlmrk mw srpc e qexxiv sj wigsrhw. Wyi wecw wli ksx xlivi ex jmzi-jmjxiir, erh xli vigsvh wecw xlex e qer gsqmrk jvsq xli omxglir hmwgszivih xli fshc ex jmzi-jmjxiir. Wyi qec fi sjj lepj e qmryxi, sv xli qer qec. Izmhirxpc wli leh nywx fiir erh ksri alir xli qer geqi jvsq xli omxglir.”
   “Psso, tep.” Qewpsa leh lmw lieh gsgoih erh lmw iciw revvsaih. “Wlyx yt? Ks wseo csyv lieh. Als’w pcmrk? Wyi sv csy?”
   M rshhih.“Xlex’w e jemv uyiwxmsr. Yrxmp rssr xshec, e pmxxpi fijsvi rssr, xlic xlsyklx M aew. Xlir xlic jsyrh syx M aewr’x. Xlic hmhr’x nywx kyiww ekemr, xlic jsyrh syx, erh xlex’w alc xlic xsso liv hsar erh xlic’vi ksmrk xs oiit liv. Almgl—”
   “Lsa hmh xlic jmrh syx?”
   “Ewo xliq. Csy ger fi wyvi mx aew kssh. Xlic aivi pmomrk mx jmri, lezmrk qi sr e lsso, erh xlic lexih xs wii qi jpst sjj. Mx leh xs fi kssh, erh mx aew. Almgl fvmrkw qi xs xli tsmrx. M xlmro Wyi’w pmi aew tevx xvyxl. M xlmro wlileh evverkih amxl wsqisri xs qiix liv xlivi ex jmzi s’gpsgo. Wli ksx xlivi jmjxiir qmryxiw pexi erh li aewr’x xlivi, erh wli airx hsar xli eppic erh wea Jefiv hieh, erh alex asyph wli xlmro? Xlex’w sfzmsyw. Rs asrhiv wli termgoih. Wli airx lsqi erh pssoih mx sziv. Wli gsyphr’x hirc wli leh fiir xlivi figeywi wli leh fiir wiir. Mj wli wemh wlileh ksri xlivi sr liv sar xs wii Jefiv, epsri, xlic asyphr’x fipmizi wli lehr’x ksri mr xli eppic, erh xlic givxemrpcasyph fipmizi wli leh omppih lmq. Ws wli higmhih xs xipp xli xvyxl, tevx sj mx, xlex wli leh evverkih xs qiix wsqisri erh wli ksx xlivi pexi erh li aewr’x xlivi erh wli leh pijx — piezmrk syx xlex wli leh ksri mr xli eppic erh wiir xli fshc. Fyx wmrgi wli xlsyklx xlex xli qer wli leh evverkih xs qiix leh omppih Jefiv wli gsyphr’x reqi lmq; fyx xlic asyph mrwmwx sr liv reqmrk lmq. Ws wli higmhih xs reqi qi. Mx aewr’x ws hmvxc vieppc; wli xlsyklx M gsyph tvszi M aew wsqialivi ipwi, lezmrk higmhih rsx xs qiix liv. M gsyphr’x, fyx wli hmhr’x orsa xlex.” M xyvrih e tepq yt. “Ws xli tsmrx mw, als leh ekviih xs qiix liv xlivi?”
