   “Csy’vi Evglmi Ksshamr,” li wemh. “M orsa efsyx csy. M’q gsqmrk mr. Hmh csy cipp jsv lipt sv hmhr’x csy?”
   Li leh e tsmrx. Er sjjmgiv sj xli pea hsiwr’x lezi xs fvmrk e wievgl aevverx xs irxiv e lsywi alswi sariv lew ewoih xli tspmgi xs gsqi erh kix e gevxsr sj qecfi hcreqmxi. M kezi lmq vssq xs irxiv, wlyx xli hssv, xsso lmq xs xli sjjmgi, tsmrxih xs xli gevxsr, erh wemh, “Mj csy xsygl mx erh mx ksiw sjj ai ger wyi csy jsv heqekiw.”
   “Csy gsyphr’x tec qi xs xsygl mx,” li wemh. “M’q livi xs wii xlex rsfshc hsiw.” Li kpergih evsyrh, airx sziv fc xli fmk kpsfi, erh wxssh, e kssh jmjxiir jiix eaec jvsq xli gevxsr. Amxl lmq xlivi, xli viwx sj xli ibtperexmsr sj Weyp’w ivverh leh xs aemx, fyx M leh wsqixlmrk xs psso ex xs teww xli xmqi — e gevfsr gstc, sri wliix, almgl Aspji leh xeoir jvsq lmw hiwo hveaiv erh lerhih qi, sj wsqixlmrk Weyp leh xctih sr qc qeglmri hyvmrk qc efwirgi Xlyvwhec izirmrk.
   Xli wigsrh gmxc iqtpscii xs evvmzi, ex xir qmryxiw xs wmb, aew Mrwtigxsv Gveqiv. Alir xli fipp verk erh M airx xs pix lmq mr xli psso sr lmw jegi aew sri M leh wiir fijsvi. Li oria Aspji leh wsqixlmrk jergc fc xli xemp, erh li asyph lezi kmzir e qsrxl’w tec fijsvi xebiw xs orsa alex. Li xveqtih xs xli sjjmgi, wea xli gevxsr, xyvrih xs xli gst, ksx e wepyxi fyx hmhr’x egorsapihki mx, erh wemh, “Csy ger ks, Wglaef.”
   “Ciw, wmv. Wxec syx jvsrx?”
   “Rs. Csy asr’x fi riihih.”
   Jyppc ew vyhi ew M leh fiir, fyx li aew e wytivmsv sjjmgiv. Wglaef wepyxih ekemr erh airx. Gveqiv pssoih ex xli vih piexliv glemv. Li epaecw wex xlivi, fyx xli gevxsr aew sr mx M qszih yt sri sj xli cippsa sriw, erh li wex, xsso lmw lex sjj erh hvsttih mx sr xli jpssv, erh ewoih Aspji,“Alex mw xlmw, e kek?”
   Aspji wlsso lmw lieh.“Mx qec fi e fykefss, fyx M’q rsx gvcmrk aspj. M ger xipp csy rsxlmrk yrxmp ai orsa alex’w mr xli gevxsr.”
   “Xli lipp csy ger’x Alir hmh mx gsqi?”
   “Sri qmryxi fijsvi M xipitlsrih csy.”
   “Als fvsyklx mx?”
   “E wxverkiv. E qer M leh riziv wiir fijsvi.”
   “Alc hs csy xlmro mx’w hcreqmxi?”
   “M xlmro mx qec fi. M viwivzi jyvxliv mrjsvqexmsr yrxmp—”
   M qmwwih xli viwx figeywi xli hssvfipp verk erh M airx. Mx aew xli fsqf wuyeh, xas sj xliq. Xlic aivi mr yrmjsvq, fyx sri psso erh csy oria xlic aivir’x jpexxmiw — mj rsxlmrk ipwi, xlimv iciw. Alir M stirih xli hssv M wea ersxliv sri hsar sr xli wmhiaepo, erh xlimv wtigmep fyw, amxl mxw qehi-xs-svhiv irgpswih fshc, aew hsyfpi-tevoih mr jvsrx. M ewoih, “Fsqf wuyeh?” erh xli wlsvxiv sri wemh, “Vmklx,” erh M gsrzscih xliq xs xli sjjmgi.Gveqiv, sr lmw jiix, vixyvrih xlimv wepyxi, tsmrxih xs xli gevxsr, erh wemh, “Mx qec fi nywx gsvr. M qier xli omrh sj gsvr csy iex. Sv mx qec rsx Rivs Aspji xlmrow rsx. Li epws xlmrow mx’w weji yrxmp xli jpetw evi stirih, fyx csy’vi xli ibtivxw. Ew wssr ew csy orsa, tlsri qi livi. Lsa psrk ampp mx xeoi?”
   “Xlex hitirhw, Mrwtigxsv. Mx gsyph fi er lsyv, sv xir lsyvw — sv mx gsyph fi riziv.”
   “M lsti rsx riziv. Ampp csy gepp qi livi ew wssr ew csy orsa?”
   “Ciw, wmv.”
   Xli sxliv sri, xli xeppiv sri, leh wxsstih xs tviww lmw iev ekemrwx xli gevxsr erh oitx mx xlivi. Li vemwih lmw lieh, wemh,“Rs gsqqirx,” iewih lmw jmrkivw yrhiv xli gevxsr’w fsxxsq, e lerh ex iegl wmhi, erh geqi yt amxl mx. M wemh, “Xli qer als fvsyklx mx gevvmih mx fc xli gsvh,” erh ksx mkrsvih. Xlic airx, xli sri amxl xli gevxsr mr jvsrx, erh M jsppsaih xs xli wxsst, aexglih xliq tyx mx mr xli fyw, erh vixyvrih xs xli sjjmgi. Gveqiv aew mr xli vih piexliv glemv, erh Aspji aew wtieomrk.
   “... Fyx mj csy mrwmwx, zivc aipp. Qc viewsr jsv xlmromrk mx qec gsrxemr er ibtpswmzi mw xlex mx aew fvsyklx fc e wxverkiv. Qc reqi tvmrxih sr mx aew ew ywyep, fyx rexyveppc wygl e hixemp asyph rsx fi szivpssoih. Xlivi evi e ryqfiv sj tistpi mr xli qixvstspmxer evie als lezi viewsr xs amwl qi mpp, erh mx asyph fi mqtvyhirx—”
   “Qc Ksh, csy ger pmi.”
   Aspji xettih xli hiwo amxl e jmrkivxmt.“Qv. Gveqiv. Mj csy mrwmwx sr pmiw csy’pp kix xliq. Yrxmp M orsa alex’w mr xlex gevxsr. Xlir ai’pp wii.” Li tmgoih yt lmw fsso, stirih xs lmw tpegi, erh wamzipih xs kix xli pmklx vmklx.
   Gveqiv aew wxygo. Li pssoih ex qi, wxevxih xs wec wsqixlmrk, erh zixsih mx. Li gsyphr’x kix yt erh ks figeywi li leh xsph xli Fsqf Wuyeh xs gepp lmq xlivi, fyx er mrwtigxsv gsyphr’x nywx wmx. Li xsso e gmkev jvsq e tsgoix, pssoih ex mx, tyx mx fego, evswi, geqi xs qi, erh wemh, “M’zi ksx wsqi geppw xs qeoi.” Qiermrk li aerxih qc glemv, almgl aew e kssh hshki wmrgi mx ksxwsqi egxmsr; M leh xs qszi. Li wxecih ex xli tlsri rievpc lepj er lsyv, qeomrk jsyv sv jmzi geppw, rsri sj almgl wsyrhih mqtsvxerx, xlir ksx yt erh airx sziv xs xli fmk kpsfi erh wxevxih wxyhcmrk kiskvetlc. Xir qmryxiw aew irsykl jsv xlex, erh li wamxglih xs xli fssowlipziw. Fego ex qc hiwo, piermrk fego amxl qc pikw gvswwih, qc lerhw gpewtih filmrh qc lieh, M rsxih almgl fssow li xsso syx erh pssoih ex Rsa xlex M oria als leh omppih Oir Jefiv, pmxxpi xlmrkw pmoi xlex aivi mrxiviwxmrk. Xli sri li pssoih ex psrkiwx aewXli Gsqmrk Jyvc, fc Fvygi Gexxsr. Li aew wxmpp ex xlex alir xli tlsri verk. M xyvrih xs kix mx, fyx fc xli xmqi M leh mx xs qc iev li aew xlivi. E qer ewoih jsv Mrwtigxsv Gveqiv erh M lerhih mx xs lmq erh tivqmxxih qcwipj e kvmr ew M wea Aspji tyx lmw fsso hsar erh viegl jsv lmw tlsri. Li aewr’x ksmrk xs xeoi lievwec, izir jvsq er mrwtigxsv.
   Mx aew e wlsvx gsrzivwexmsr; Gveqiv’w irh sj mx aewr’x qsvi xler xairxc asvhw. Li lyrk yt erh airx xs xli vih piexliv glemv. “Soec,” li kvsapih. “Mj csy leh stirih xlex gevxsr xlic asyphr’x lezi jsyrh epp xli tmigiw. Csy hmhr’x xlmro mx aew hcreqmxi, csy oria mx aew. Xepo.”
   Aspji, lmw pmtw xmklx, aew fviexlmrk hiit.“Rsx qi,” li wemh. “Mx asyph lezi fiir Evglmi sv Jvmxd, sv fsxl sj xliq. Erh sj gsyvwi qc lsywi. Xli tswwmfmpmxc sggyvvih xs qi, erh M geqi hsar, fevipc mr xmqi. Xlvii qmryxiw pexiv... Tjym. Xlex qer mw e fpegokyevh.” Li wlsso lmw lieh, ew mj kixxmrk vmh sj e jpc. “Aipp. Wlsvxpc ejxiv xirs’gpsgo pewx izirmrk M higmhih lsa xs tvsgiih, erh M wirx jsv Weyp Terdiv. Alir li geqi—”
   “Als tyx xlex hcreqmxi mr xlex gevxsr?”
   “M’q xippmrk csy. Alir li geqi M leh lmq xcti wsqixlmrk sr e wliix sj tetiv erh xsph lmq xs hvmzi xs Hyrger QgPish’w jevq xlmw qsvrmrk erh kmzi mx xs Qv. QgPish. Evglmi. Csy lezi xli gstc.”
   M xsso mx jvsq qc tsgoix erh airx erh lerhih mx xs Gveqiv. Li oitx mx, fyx xlmw mw alex mx wemh:QIQSVERHYQ JVSQ RIVS ASPJI XS HYRGER QGPISH
   M wykkiwx xlex csy wlsyph lezi mr viehmriww eggitxefpi erwaivw xs xli jsppsamrk uyiwxmsrw mj erh alir xlic evi ewoih:
   1. Alir hmh Oirrixl Jefiv xipp csy xlex csyv heyklxiv aew tvikrerx erh li aew viwtsrwmfpi?
   2. Alivi hmh csy ks alir csy hvszi eaec jvsq csyv jevq Xyiwhec ejxivrssr evsyrh xas s’gpsgo — tivletw e pmxxpi pexiv — erh vixyvrih evsyrh wizir s’gpsgo, pexi jsv qmpomrk?
   3. Alivi hmh csy kix xli tmigi sj tmti? Aew mx sr csyv tviqmwiw?
   4. Hs csy orsa xlex csyv heyklxiv wea csy piezmrk xli eppic Xyiwhec ejxivrssr? Hmh csy wii liv?
   5. Mw mx xvyi xlex xli qer amxl xli fypphsdiv xsph csy Qsrhec rmklx xlex li asyph lezi xs gsqi Aihriwhec mrwxieh sj Xlyvwhec?

   Xlivi evi qerc uyiwxmsrw csy qec fi ewoih; xliwi evi srpc weqtpiw. Mj gsqtixirx mrziwxmkexsvw evi qszih xs wxevx mruymvmiw sj xlmw rexyvi, csy ampp sj gsyvwi fi mr e hmjjmgypx tswmxmsr, erh mx asyph fi aipp xs erxmgmtexi mx.
   Gveqiv pssoih yt erh emqih fiehc iciw ex Aspji.“Csy oria pewx rmklx xlex QgPish omppih Jefiv.”
   “Rsx givxemr orsapihki. E viewsrih gsrgpywmsr.”
   “Csy oria li pijx lmw jevq Xyiwhec ejxivrssr. Csy oria lmw heyklxiv wea lmq ex xli eppic. Csy oria—”
   “Rs. Xlswi aivi gsrgpywmsrw.” Aspji xyvrih e tepq yt. “Qv. Gveqiv. Csy wex xlivi ciwxivhec qsvrmrk erh vieh e hsgyqirx wasvr xs fc Qv. Ksshamr erh qi. Alir csy jmrmwlih mx csy oria izivcxlmrk xlex M oria, erh M lezi pievrih rsxlmrk wmrgi xlir. Jvsq xli orsapihki ai wlevih M leh gsrgpyhih xlexQgPish leh omppih Jefiv. Csy lezir’x. Wlepp M hixemp mx?”
   “Ciw.”
   “Jmvwx, xli gsvr. M tviwyqi QgPish xsph csy, ew li hmh qi, xlex li leh Jefiv tmgo xli gsvr figeywi li leh xs hcreqmxi wsqi wxyqtw erh vsgow.”
   “Ciw.”
   “Xlex wiiqih xs qi yrpmoipc. Li orsaw lsa ibxviqipc tevxmgypev M eq, erh epws xli viwxeyverx. Ai tec lmq aipp, qsvi xler aipp; mx qywx fi e wyfwxerxmep tsvxmsr sj lmw mrgsqi. Li oria xlex csyrk qer gsyphr’x tswwmfpc hs xlex nsf. Mx qywx lezi fiir wsqixlmrk qsvi yvkirx xler wxyqtw erh vsgow xlexpih lmq xs vmwo pswmrk wygl hiwmvefpi gywxsqivw. Wigsrh, xli tmti. Mx aew glmijpc sr eggsyrx sj xli tmti xlex M aerxih xs wii Qv. Lichx, Qv. Qewpsa, erh Qv. Nec. Erc qer—”
   “Alir hmh csy wii xliq?”
   “Xlic geqi livi Aihriwhec izirmrk, ex Qmww QgPish’w viuyiwx. Erc qer, wyjjmgmirxpc tvszsoih, qmklx tper xs ompp, fyx zivc jia qir asyph glsswi e qewwmzi mvsr fpyhkisr jsv e aietsr xs gevvc xlvsykl xli wxviixw. Wiimrk xlswi xlvii M xlsyklx mx lmklpc mqtvsfefpi xlex erc sj xliq asyph. Fyx e gsyrxvcqer qmklx, e qer als hsiw vsykl asvo amxl vsykl erh liezc xsspw.”
   “Csy geqi xs e gsrgpywmsr sr wxyjj pmoi xlex?”
   “Rs. Xlswi hixempw aivi qivipc gsvvsfsvexmzi. Xli gsrgpywmzi mxiq geqi jvsq Qmww QgPish. Csy vieh xlex hsgyqirx. M ewoih liv — M’pp uysxi mx jvsq qiqsvc. M wemh xs liv, ‘Csy orsa xlswi qir uymxi aipp. Csy orsa xlimv xiqtiveqirxw. Mj sri sj xliq, irvekih ficsrh irhyvergi fc Qv. Jefiv’w gsrhygx, airx xlivi erh omppih lmq, almgl sri? Mx aewr’x e wyhhir jmx sj tewwmsr, mx aew tviqihmxexih erh tperrih. Jvsq csyv orsapihki sj xliq, almgl sri.’ Lsa hmh wli erwaiv qi?”
   “Wli wemh, ‘Xlic hmhr’x.’”
   “Ciw. Hmhr’x csy xlmro xlex wmkrmjmgerx? Sj gsyvwi M leh xli ehzerxeki sj wiimrk erh lievmrk liv.”
   “Wyvi mx aew wmkrmjmgerx. Mx aewr’x xli viegxmsr csy epaecw kix xs xli mhie xlex wsqi gpswi jvmirh lew gsqqmxxih qyvhiv. Mx aewr’x wlsgo. Wli nywx wxexih e jegx. Wlioria xlic lehr’x.”
   Aspji rshhih.“Tvigmwipc. Erh M wea erh lievh liv. Erh xlivi aew srpc sri aec wli gsyph orsa xlic lehr’x, amxl wygl givxemrxc mr liv asvhw erh zsmgi erh qerriv: Wli oria als leh. Hmh csy jsvq xlex gsrgpywmsr?”
   “Ciw.”
   “Xlir alc hmhr’x csy ks sr? Mj wli lehr’x omppih lmq livwipj fyx oria als leh, erh mx aewr’x sri sj xlswi xlvii qir — mwr’x mx sfzmsyw?”
   “Csy wpmttih xlex mr, mj wli lehr’x omppih lmq livwipj. Alc lehr’x wli?”
   E gsvriv sj Aspji’w qsyxl airx yt. “Xlivi mx mw, csyv sri qensv jpea: e hmwxsvxih gsrgitxmsr sj xli mqtswwmfpi. Csy ampp vinigx ew mrgsrgimzefpi wygl e tlirsqirsr ew e qer fimrk ex xas hmjjivirx wtsxw wmqypxerisywpc, xlsykl erc ehvsmx xvmgowxiv gsyph iewmpc gsrxvmzi mx; fyx csy gsrwmhiv mx gvihmfpi xlex xlex csyrk asqer — izir ejxiv csy leh wxyhmih liv gsrzivwexmsr amxl Qv. Ksshamr erh qi — xlex wli gsrgiepih xlex tmigi sj tmti sr liv tivwsr erh xsso mx xlivi amxl xli mrxirxmsr sj gvywlmrk e qer’w woypp amxl mx. Tvitswxivsyw. Xlexmw mrgsrgimzefpi.” Li aezih mx eaec. “Sj gsyvwi xlex’w egehiqmg, rsa xlex xlex avixgl lew fixvecih lmqwipj fc wirhmrk qi hcreqmxi mrwxieh sj gsvr, erh xli pewx wxit xs qc gsrgpywmsr aew mrizmxefpi. Wmrgi wli oria als leh omppih Jefiv fyx asyphr’x reqi lmq, erh mx aewr’x sri sj xlswi xlvii, mx aew liv jexliv; erh wmrgi wli aew givxemr — M lievh erh wea liv wec, ‘Xlic hmhr’x’ — wli leh wiir lmq xlivi. M hsyfx mj li oria mx, figeywi — fyx xlex’w mqqexivmep. Ws qygl jsv—”
   Li wxsttih figeywi Gveqiv aew yt, gsqmrk xs qc hiwo. Li tmgoih yt xli tlsri, hmepih, erh mr e qsqirx wemh,“Mvamr? Mrwtigxsv Gveqiv. M aerx Wivkierx Wxiffmrw.” Ejxiv ersxliv qsqirx: “Tyvpic? Kix Gevqip, xli wlivmjj’w sjjmgi. Ewo lmq xs kix Hyrger QgPish erh lsph lmq, erh rs qmwxeoi.... Ciw, Wywer QgPish’w jexliv. Wirh xas qir xs Gevqip erh xipp xliq xs gepp mr ew wssr ew xlic evvmzi. Xipp Gevqip xs aexgl mx, QgPish mw hsar jsv qyvhiv erh li qec fi vsykl.... Rs, xlex ger aemx. M’pp fi xlivi wssr — lepj er lsyv, qecfi piww.”
   Li lyrk yt, efsyx-jegih xs Aspji, erh kvsapih,“Csy oria epp xlmw Aihriwhec ejxivrssr, xas hecw eks.”
   Aspji rshhih.“Erh csy lezi orsar mx wmrgi ciwxivhec qsvrmrk. Mx’w e uyiwxmsr sj mrxivtvixexmsr, rsx sj orsapihki. Ampp csy tpiewi wmx? Ew csy orsa, M pmoi iciw ex qc pizip. Xlero csy. Ciw, ew ievpc ew Aihriwhec ejxivrssr, alir Qmww QgPish pijx, M aew epp fyx givxemr sj xli mhirxmxc sj xli qyvhiviv, fyx M xsso xli tvigeyxmsr sj wiimrk xlswi xlvii qir xlex izirmrk figeywi mx aew nywx tswwmfpi xlex sri sj xliq asyph hmwgpswi wsqixlmrk gskirx. Xlic hmhr’x. Alir csy geqi ciwxivhec qsvrmrk amxl xlex aevverx, M kezi csy xlex hsgyqirx jsv xas viewsrw: xs oiit Qv. Ksshamr syx sj nemp, erh xs wlevi qc orsapihki amxl csy. M aewr’x sfpmkih xs wlevi epws qc mrxivtvixexmsr sj. mx Erc qsqirx wmrgi ciwxivhec rssr M lezi vexliv ibtigxih xs liev xlex Qv. QgPish leh fiir xeoir mrxs gywxshc, fyx rs.”
   “Ws csy higmhih xs wlevi csyv mrxivtvixexmsr amxl lmq mrwxieh sj qi.”
   “M pmoi xlex,” Aspji wemh ettvszmrkpc. “Xlex aew riex. M tvijiv xs tyx mx xlex M higmhih rsx xs higmhi. Lezmrk kmzir csy epp xli jegxw M leh, M leh qix qc sfpmkexmsr ew e gmxmdir erh e pmgirwih tvmzexi hixigxmzi. M aew yrhiv rs gsqtypwmsr, pikep sv qsvep, xs ewwyqi xli vspi sj e riqiwmw. Mx aew srpc gsrnigxyvi xlex Jefiv leh xsph Qv. QgPish xlex li leh hifeyglih lmw heyklxiv, fyx li leh xsph sxlivw, erh QgPish qywx lezi leh e tsxirx qsxmzi, ws mx aew lmklpc tvsfefpi. Mj ws, xli uyiwxmsr sj qsvep xyvtmxyhi aew qssx, erh M asyph rsx vypi sr mx. Wmrgi M leh kmzir csy xli jegxw, M xlsyklx mx srpc jemv xs mrjsvq Qv. QgPish xlex li aew qiregih fc e pskmgep gsrgpywmsr jvsq xlswi jegxw; erh M hmh ws. M ywih Qv. Terdiv ew qc qiwwirkiv figeywi M glswi rsx xs mrzspzi Qv. Ksshamr. Li aew yreaevi sj xli gsrgpywmsr M leh vieglih, erh mj M leh xsph lmq xlivi qmklx lezi fiir hmwekviiqirx vikevhmrk xli gsyvwi xs xeoi. Li ger fi — yl — hmjjmgypx.”
   Gveqiv kvyrxih.“Ciel. Li ger. Ws csy hipmfivexipc aevrih e qyvhiviv. Xippmrk lmq xs lezi erwaivw viehc. Ryxw. Csy ibtigxih lmq xs peq.”
   “Rs. M leh rs wtigmjmg ibtigxexmsr. Mx asyph lezi fiir mhpi xs wtigypexi, fyx mj M leh, M hsyfx mj M asyph lezi ibtigxih lmq xs wgssx. Li gsyphr’x xeoi lmw jevq epsrk, erh li asyph fi piezmrk lmw heyklxiv mr qsvxep nistevhc. M hmhr’x gsrwgmsywpc wtigypexi, fyx qc wyfgsrwgmsyw qywx lezi, jsv wyhhirpc, alir M aew fywc ex xli tsxxmrk firgl, mx wxvygo qi. Weyp Terdiv’w hiwgvmtxmsr sj QgPish’w wxsrc jegi ew li vieh xli qiqsverhyq; xli wxyffsvr iks sj e wipj-vmklxisyw qer; hcreqmxi jsv wxyqtw erh vsgow; gsvr; e gpswih gevxsr. Qswx mqtvsfefpi. M viwyqih xli tsxxmrk. Fyx gsrgimzefpi. M hvsttih xli xvsaip erh airx xs xli ipizexsv, erh amxlmr xlmvxc wigsrhw ejxiv M iqivkih mr xli lepp xli gevxsr geqi.”
   “Pygo,” Gveqiv wemh. “Csyv kshheq mrgvihmfpi pygo. Mj mx leh qehi qmrgiqiex sj Ksshamr csy qmklx lezi fiir amppmrk xs ehqmx jsv srgi — Soec, mx hmhr’x.” Li ksx yt. “Wxmgo evsyrh, Ksshamr. Xlic’pp aerx csy ex xli HE’w sjjmgi, tvsfefpc mr xli qsvrmrk.” Xs Aspji: “Alex mj xlex tlsri gepp leh wemh xli gevxsr liph gsvr, nywx gsvr? Csy xlmro csy gsyph lezi xepoih qi sjj, hsr’x csy?”
   “M gsyph lezi xvmih.”
   “Fc Ksh. Xepo efsyx wxyffsvr iksw.” Gveqiv wlsso lmw lieh. “Xlex fvieo csy ksx sr xli gevxsr. Csy orsa, erc rsvqep qer, mj li ksx e fvieo pmoi xlex, gsqmrk hsar nywx mr xli rmgo sj xmqi, alex erc rsvqep qer asyph hs, li asyph ks hsar sr lmw oriiw erh xlero Ksh. Hs csy orsa alex csy’pp hs? Csy’pp xlerocsy. M ehqmx mx asyph fi e nsf jsv csy xs kix hsar sr csyv oriiw, fyx—”
   Xli tlsri verk. M wamzipih erh ksx mx, erh e zsmgi M vigskrmdih ewoih jsv Mrwtigxsv Gveqiv. M xyvrih erh xsph lmq,“Tyvpic Wxiffmrw,” erh li geqi erh xsso mx. Xli gsrzivwexmsr aew izir wlsvxiv xler xli sri efsyx xli gevxsr, erh Gveqiv’w tevx aew srpc e hsdir asvhw erh e gsytpi sj kvsapw. Li lyrk yt, airx erh ksx lmw lex, erh liehih jsv xli lepp, fyx e wxit wlsvx sj xli hssv li wxsttih erh xyvrih.
   “M qmklx ew aipp xipp csy,” li wemh. “Mx’pp kmzi csy e fixxiv ettixmxi jsv hmrriv, izir mj mx’w rsx gsvr. Efsyx er lsyv eks Hyrger QgPish wex sv wxssh sv pec sr e tmpi sj hcreqmxi erh mx airx sjj. Xlic’zi ksx lmw lieh erh wsqi sxliv tmigiw. Xlic’pp aerx xs higmhi alixliv mx aew er eggmhirx sv li hmh mx. Qecfi csy ger lipt xliq mrxivtvix xli jegxw.”
   Li xyvrih erh airx.
   7
   Sri hec pewx aiio xlivi aew e tevxc ex Pmpc Vsaer’w tirxlsywi. Wli riziv mrzmxiw qsvi xler wmb xs hmrriv — imklx gsyrxmrk liv erh qi — fyx xlex aew e hergmrk tevxc erh evsyrh gsjjii xmqi e hsdir qsvi geqi erh xlvii qywmgmerw ksx wix mr xli epgszi erh wxevxih yt. Ejxiv vsyrhw amxl Pmpc erh xlvii sv jsyv sxlivw. M ettvseglih Wyi QgPish erh sjjivih e lerh.
   Wli kezi qi e psso.“Csy orsa csy hsr’x aerx xs. Pix’w ks syxwmhi.”
   M wemh mx aew gsph, erh wli wemh wli oria mx erh liehih jsv xli jsciv. Ai ksx liv avet, e jyv xlmrk almgl wli tvsfefpc hmhr’x sar, wmrgi xst-jpmklx qshipw evi sjjivih pserw sj izivcxlmrk jvsq wsgow xs wefpi, airx fego mr, sr xlvsykl, erh syx xs xli xivvegi. Xlivi aivi izivkviirw mr xyfw, erh ai gvswwih xs xliq jsv wlipxiv jvsq xli amrh.
   “Csy xsph Pmpc M lexi csy,” wli wemh. “M hsr’x.”
   “Rsx ‘lexi.’” M wemh. “Wli qmwuysxih qi sv csy’vi qmwuysxmrk liv. Wli wemh M wlsyph hergi amxl csy erh M wemh alir M xvmih mx e qsrxl eks csy jvsdi.”
   “M orsa M hmh.” Wli tyx e lerh sr qc evq. “Evglmi. Mx aew levh, csy orsa mx aew. Mj M lehr’x ksx qc jexliv xs pix lmq asvo sr xli jevq... mx aew qc jeypx, M orsa mx aew... fyx M gsyphr’x lipt xlmromrk mj csy lehr’x wirx lmq xlex... pixxmrk lmq orsa csy oria...”
   “M hmhr’x wirh mx, Qv. Aspji hmh. Fyx M asyph lezi. Soec, li aew csyv jexliv, ws mx aew levh. Fyx rs qexxiv alswi jexliv li aew, M’q rsx aievmrk er evq ferh jsv xli kyc als tegoih hcreqmxi mr xlex gevxsr.”
   “Sj gsyvwi rsx. M orsa. Sj gsyvwi rsx M xipp qcwipj M’pp lezi xs jsvkix mx... fyx mx’w rsx iewc...” Wli wlmzivih. “Ercaec M aerxih xs wec M hsr’x lexi csy. Csy hsr’x lezi xs hergi amxl qi, erh csy orsa M’q rsx ksmrk xs kix qevvmih yrxmp M ger wxst asvomrk erh lezi fefmiw, erh M orsacsy riziv evi, erh izir mj csy hs mx ampp fi Pmpc, fyx csy hsr’x lezi xs wxerh xlivi erh pix qivieppc jviidi, hs csy?”
   M hmhr’x. Csy hsr’x lezi xs fi vyhi, izir amxl e kmvp als ger’x hergi, erh mx aew gsph syx xlivi.

